s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fr7M9w%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Income%20difference%20between%20bachelor's%20and%20graduate%20degree%20pay%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22904%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feducationdata.org%2Faverage-cost-of-a-masters-degree%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEducation%20Data%20Initiative%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20a%20graduate%20degree%20on%20average%20costs%20between%20%2454%2C000%20and%20%2473%2C000%2C%20depending%20on%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20school%20and%20area%20of%20study.%20Between%20the%201989-90%20academic%20year%20and%20the%202020-21%20one%2C%20graduate-school%20tuition%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feducationdata.org%2Fcollege-tuition-inflation-rate%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFrom%2520the%25201989%252D90%2520academic%2Ctuition%2520inflation%2520rate%2520is%25201.82%2525.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreased%20nearly%205%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20year.%20Some%20top%20law%20schools%20cost%20over%20%24200%2C000%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20program%2C%20while%20medical%20schools%20average%20nearly%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feducationdata.org%2Faverage-cost-of-medical-school%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24219%2C000%20a%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20San%20Jose-Sunnyvale-Santa%20Clara%20metropolitan%20area%20had%20an%20average%20income%20difference%20of%20over%20%2448%2C000%20between%20a%20graduate%20and%20bachelor's%20degree%20%E2%80%94%20%24150%2C000%20versus%20%24102%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20SmartAsset.%20San%20Jose%20graduate-degree%20holders%20made%20about%20%2430%2C000%20more%20than%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20which%20had%20the%20next-biggest%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuntsville%20had%20an%20avera