Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F21185309%2FFBIHoover.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F21185309%2FFBIHoover.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F21185309%2FFBIHoover-300x214.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F21185309%2FFBIHoover-1024x731.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468208%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22857%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJ.%20Edgar%20Hoover.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FFBI%2C%20Public%20Domain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20car%20of%20the%20Shin%20Bet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%2C%20for%20example%2C%20violence%20was%20allowed%20to%20deteriorate%20in%20the%20plant%20nursery%20of%20Muhammad%20Mahmada%2C%20near%20the%20village%20of%20As-Sawiya%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%20Between%202021%20and%202022%2C%20Mahmada%20suffered%20from%20repeated%20incidents%20of%20theft%20and%20vandalism%20by%20%E2%80%9CHilltop%20Youth%E2%80%9D%20who%20repeatedly%20came%20to%20his%20plant%20nursery%2C%20using%20the%20same%20vehicle.%20The%20far-right%20activists%20and%20their%20vehicle%20were%20clearly%20visible%20in%20the%20plant%20nursery%E2%80%99s%20security%20camera%20footage%2C%20and%20the%20settlement%20Ariel%20police%20received%20a%20report%20that%20some%20of%20the%20stolen%20trees%20were%20planted%20at%20the%20entrance%20to%20the%20Rehelim%20settlement%2C%20and%20that%20the%20vehicle%20used%20in%20the%20incidents%20was%20seen%20in%20that%20settlement.%20They%20were%20not%20arrested.%20The%20law%20was%20not%20enforced%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20Mahmada%20managed%20to%20catch%20the%20far-right%20activists%20on%20his%20own%2C%20the%20fifth%20time%20they%20came%20to%20his%20plant%20nursery%20to%20carry%20out%20their%20plan.%20Although%20it%20is%20the%20same%20cell%20of%20%E2%80%9CHilltop%20Youth%E2%80%9D%20that%20operated%2C%20the%20prosecution%20unit%20filed%20only%20one%20indictment%20against%20one%20of%20them%2C%20and%20only%20on%20one%20of%20the%20recurring%20incidents.%20The%20charge%20was%20for%20theft%2C%20the%20defendant%20was%20not%20attributed%20membership%20of%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%2C%20nor%20a%20racial%20motive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20the%20unusual%20conduct%20was%20revealed%20in%20an%20investigation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.ynet.co.il%2Farticles%2Frjcwgftcf%3Futm_source%3Dmivzakimnet%26utm_medium%3Dmobile%26utm_campaign%3Dmivzakimnet%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Israeli%20journalist%20Elisha%20Ben-Kimon%20on%20February%204%2C%202022%20%E2%80%93%20the%20vehicle%20used%20in%20the%20chain%20of%20incidents%20in%20Mahmada%E2%80%99s%20plant%20nursery%20belonged%20to%20the%20Shin%20Bet.%20A%20Shin%20Bet%20agent%20who%20was%20implanted%20in%20the%20cell%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CHilltop%20Youth%E2%80%9D%20participated%20in%20the%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20complaint%20submitted%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20state%20prosecutor%20for%20special%20duties%20against%20the%20Shin%20Bet%2C%20on%20June%202022%2C%20he%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Crecently%20a%20response%20was%20received%20from%20some%20of%20the%20parties%20to%20whom%20the%20complaint%20was%20forwarded.%20In%20view%20of%20the%20content%20of%20the%20response%20received%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20deepen%20the%20investigation%20and%20forward%20your%20request%20to%20additional%20parties%20in%20order%20to%20exhaust%20the%20investigation.%20Another%20update%20will%20be%20sent%20after%20all%20the%20responses%20have%20been%20examined%20and%20when%20a%20decision%20has%20been%20made%20on%20them.%E2%80%9D%20Mahmada%20has%20been%20waiting%20for%20this%20decision%20for%20over%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20the%20Israel%20Police%20continued%20to%20act%20negligently%2C%20did%20not%20recognise%20the%20incidents%20as%20terrorist%20incidents%2C%20and%20the%20deputy%20state%20prosecutor%20for%20special%20duties%20continued%20to%20drag%20his%20feet%20in%20investigating%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20Shin%20Bet.%20Therefore%2C%20perhaps%20it%20is%20no%20wonder%20that%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20December%2019%2C%202022%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kan.org.il%2Fcontent%2Fkan-news%2Fdefense%2F245069%2F%5C%22%3Esixth%20incident%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20place%20at%20Mahmada%E2%80%99s%20plant%20nursery%2C%20which%20was%20a%20step%20up%20in%20violence.%20The%20%E2%80%9CHilltop%20Youth%E2%80%9D%20cell%20arrived%20again%2C%20made%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20wall%20of%20the%20building%20with%20a%20hammer%20and%20entered%20through%20it%2C%20stole%20the%20security%20camera%20and%20associated%20apparatus%20and%20other%20property%20and%20set%20fire%20to%20the%20building.%20Worst%20of%20all%2C%20they%20tried%20to%20insert%20a%20gas%20tank%20into%20the%20building%20they%20set%20fire%20to.%20The%20gas%20tank%20got%20stuck%20in%20the%20hole%20they%20made%20in%20the%20wall.%20Only%20by%20a%20miracle%20did%20the%20gas%20tank%20nor%20the%20whole%20building%20explode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F27083345%2F24545212292_5d8738816b_c.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22799%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F27083345%2F24545212292_5d8738816b_c.jpg%20799w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F27083345%2F24545212292_5d8738816b_c-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-641988%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20the%20Israel%20Palestine%20frontier.%20Photo%3A%20J%C3%BCrg%20Fraefel%2FFlickr%20(CC%20BY-NC-ND%202.0)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20the%20Shin%20Bet%E2%80%99s%20method%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20to%20Elisha%20Yered%3A%20a%20review%20of%20additional%20investigation%20files%20shows%20that%20the%20Yered%20and%20Mahmada%20cases%20are%20not%20unusual%2C%20and%20this%20Shin%20Bet%20method%20is%20also%20used%20for%20other%20far-right%20activists.%20The%20Shin%20Bet%20regularly%20gathers%20information%20about%20the%20terrorist%20activities%20of%20the%20far-right%20activists%2C%20through%20agents%20and%20collaborators%20and%20also%20in%20other%20ways%2C%20but%20refrains%20from%20stopping%20such%20activity%20in%20real-time%20or%20sharing%20evidence%20with%20the%20police%20that%20would%20allow%20them%20to%20be%20prosecuted%20%E2%80%93%20except%20in%20exceptional%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20way%2C%20when%20one%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CHilltop%20Youth%E2%80%9D%20is%20taken%20for%20questioning%2C%20the%20Shin%20Bet%20investigators%20can%20lay%20out%20before%20him%20all%20the%20terrorist%20incidents%20that%20they%20know%20he%20was%20involved%20in%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20%E2%80%9Csurprised%E2%80%9D%20suspect%20can%20%E2%80%9Cchoose%E2%80%9D%20whether%20to%20admit%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20specific%20incident%20for%20which%20he%20was%20arrested%20or%20be%20prosecuted%20for%20the%20multitude%20of%20terror%20incidents%20that%20the%20Shin%20Bet%20knows%20about%20%E2%80%93%20and%20sometimes%20to%20consider%20whether%20to%20become%20a%20collaborator%20of%20the%20Shin%20Bet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20emerges%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nevo.co.il%2Fpsika_html%2Fmechozi%2FME-16-01-932-22.htm%5C%22%3Efacts%20of%20the%20indictment%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20against%20Amiram%20Ben%20Uliel%20who%20was%20convicted%20of%20murdering%20the%20members%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F2022-09-01%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fisrael-supreme-court-rejects-appeal-of-israeli-who-murdered-palestinian-family-in-2015%2F00000182-f785-d67e-a5a3-f7cd11c60000%5C%22%3EDawabsha%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20setting%20on%20fire%20their%20home%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20town%20of%20Duma%2C%20south%20of%20Nablus%2C%20while%20they%20were%20sleeping.%20There%20it%20is%20stated%20that%20he%20was%20known%20to%20the%20Shin%20Bet%20and%20operated%20for%20two%20years%20prior%20to%20the%20incident%20as%20part%20of%20a%20new%20terror%20cell%20of%20far-right%20activists%20who%20sought%20to%20promote%20an%20extreme%20and%20violent%20ideological%20concept%20aimed%20at%20destabilising%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20through%20the%20use%20of%20terrorism%20and%20violence%2C%20including%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20it%20is%20implied%20in%20the%20indictment%20filed%20against%20Ben%20Uliel%20that%20the%20Shin%20Bet%20did%20not%20stop%20his%20terror%20cell%20in%20real%20time.%20At%20a%20closed%20conference%20of%20the%20Likud%20Party%E2%80%99s%20youth%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20the%20then%20minister%20of%20defence%20Moshe%20%E2%80%9CBogie%E2%80%9D%20Ya%E2%80%99alon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ynetnews.com%2Farticles%2F0%2C7340%2CL-4699818%2C00.html%5C%22%3Eadmitted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20security%20services%20knew%20who%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20Dawabsha%20family%E2%80%99s%20home%20but%20avoided%20prosecuting%20him%20so%20as%20not%20to%20reveal%20intelligence%20sources%20in%20the%20court.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20in%20view%20of%20the%20tremendous%20public%20and%20political%20pressure%20exerted%20on%20Israel%20following%20the%20shock%20of%20the%20murder%20of%20parents%20and%20their%20one-and-a-half-year-old%20son%2C%20an%20indictment%20was%20filed%20against%20Ben%20Uliel%20and%20another%20suspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20this%20modus%20operandi%20of%20the%20Shin%20Bet%20reduce%20Israeli%20far-right%20terrorism%20or%20encourage%20it%20and%20give%20such%20activists%20a%20free%20hand%3F%20Since%20there%20is%20no%20transparency%20regarding%20the%20activities%20of%20the%20Shin%20Bet%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20make%20an%20overall%20objective%20assessment.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20who%20is%20paying%20the%20price.%20This%20is%20an%20experiment%20on%20Palestinian%20human%20beings%20who%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20are%20not%20recognised%20by%20most%20of%20the%20Israeli%20media%20and%20public%20as%20human%20beings%2C%20and%20therefore%20the%20experiment%20on%20them%20can%20continue%20without%20interruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAttorney%20Eitay%20Mack%20represents%20%3C%2Fem%3EMahmada%20%3Cem%3Eand%20other%20Palestinian%20victims%20of%20Israeli%20far-right%20terrorism%20together%20with%20the%20Israeli%20human%20rights%20organisation%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tag-meir.org.il%2Fen%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETag-Meir%20Forum%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the7eye.org.il%2F494339%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Earticle%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0first%20appeared%20on%20the%20Hebrew%20media%20platform%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the7eye.org.il%2Fabout%2Fenglish%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Seventh%20Eye%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693402242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-shin-bet-targets-far-right-terrorism%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20title%20that%20the%20Israeli%20media%20attaches%20to%20suspects%20of%20far-right%20terrorism%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%26quot%3Ba%20target%20of%20the%20Shin%20Bet%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%93%20sometimes%20means%20exactly%20the%20opposite%20of%20what%20we%20think.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-shin-bet-targets-far-right-terrorism%22%2C%22cdnAmpU