0getting%20schoolwork%20done%2C%20watching%20Netflix%2C%20and%20just%20generally%20browsing%20the%20web.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDell%20XPS%2013%20(2020)%20specifications%20(as%20reviewed)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisplay%20size%20and%20resolution%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2013.4%20inch%201%2C920%20x%201%2C200%20touchscreen%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EProcessor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%2011th%20generation%20Intel%20Core%20i7%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMemory%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2016GB%20RAM%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStorage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20512GB%20SSD%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPorts%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202%20USB%20Type-C%2C%20microSD%20card%20reader%2C%203.5mm%20headphone%20jack%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAuthentication%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Fingerprint%20reader%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202.8%20pounds%20(for%20touch)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWebcam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20720p%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20life%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Estimated%20up%20to%2014%20hours%20and%2011%20minutes%20(about%206%20hours%20in%20real%20world%20usage)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%20and%20display%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223622%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dell%20XPS%2013%20Lid%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fd7e66f78a5740019a15662%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222716%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Eadicicco%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dell%20XPS%2013's%20design%20is%20one%20of%20its%20most%20compelling%20characteristics.The%20model%20I've%20been%20reviewing%20weighs%202.8%20pounds%2C%20but%20that%20could%20vary%20slightly%20depending%20on%20the%20configuration.%20That%20means%20it's%20about%20the%20same%20weight%20as%20the%20HP%20Envy%2013%20and%20Apple%20MacBook%20Air.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20really%20the%20Dell%20XPS%2013's%20stunning%20screen%20that%20makes%20it%20stand%20out%20in%20terms%20of%20design.%20Dell's%20XPS%2013%20comes%20with%20a%20super-slim%20border%20framing%20its%20screen%20that%20feels%20like%20it's%20barely%20there%2C%20a%20design%20element%20that's%20defined%20the%20lineup%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20part%20of%20what%20makes%20the%20Dell%20XPS%2013%20feel%20so%20compact%2C%20even%20more%20so%20than%20other%20similarly-sized%20laptops%2C%20and%20it%20gives%20the%20XPS%2013%20a%20sleeker%20look%20compared%20to%20many%20of%20its%20rivals.%20Even%20Apple's%20MacBook%20Air%20and%20MacBook%20Pro%2C%20which%20were%20recently%20upgraded%20with%20Apple's%20fast%20new%20M1%20chips%2C%20still%20have%20noticeably%20thick%20borders%20surrounding%20their%20displays.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20offers%20the%20XPS%2013%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20display%20options.%20The%20cheapest%20configuration%20comes%20with%20a%201%2C920%20x%201%2C200%20resolution%20screen%2C%20but%20you%20can%20upgrade%20to%20a%20touch%20screen%20and%20opt%20for%20a%20higher-resolution%203%2C840%20x%202%2C400%20display.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20configuration%20I've%20been%20testing%20comes%20with%20an%20impressive%201%2C920%20x%201%2C200%20resolution%20touchscreen%2C%20which%20I%20imagine%20will%20be%20more%20than%20enough%20for%20most%20shoppers.%20Colors%20looked%20vivid%20and%20rich%20with%20crisp%20detail%2C%20and%20skin%20tones%20looked%20vibrant%20and%20true-to-life.%20It's%20exactly%20what%20you%20would%20expect%20from%20a%20premium%20laptop.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20image%20quality%20on%20the%20Dell%20XPS%2013%20was%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20the%20Apple%20MacBook%20Air%20(M1)%2C%20which%20has%20a%202%2C560%20x%201%2C600%20Retina%20display%20with%20the%20company's%20True%20Tone%20tech.%20The%20colorful%20cakes%20and%20baked%20goods%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Great%20British%20Baking%20Show%26quot%3B%20looked%20just%20as%20vibrant%20(and%20appetizing)%20on%20both%20laptops%2C%20with%20very%20minor%20and%20barely%20noticeable%20differences%20between%20the%20two.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dell%20XPS%2013%20comes%20with%20two%20USB-C%20ports%2C%20a%20headphone%20jack%2C%20and%20a%20microSD%20card%20slot.%20That's%20probably%20enough%20for%20most%20people%2C%20but%20the%20lack%20of%20selection%20could%20be%20a%20drawback%20for%20anyone%20looking%20to%20use%20older%20accessories%20without%20a%20hub%20or%20adapter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerformance%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dell%20XPS%2013%20top%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fd7e6e62069f400194c7b8e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Eadicicco%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dell%20XPS%2013%20is%20more%20than%20capable%20of%20breezing%20through%20everyday%20tasks%20with%20ease%2C%20as%20I%20learned%20after%20using%20it%20as%20my%20primary%20work%20machine.%20My%20review%20configuration%20includes%20an%2011th-generation%20Intel%20Core%20i7%20processor%20with%2016GB%20of%20memory%20(RAM)%20and%20512GB%20of%20solid-state%20drive%20(SSD)%20storage%2C%20a%20system%20that%20currently%20cost%20%241%2C469.99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20workload%20usually%20consists%20of%20running%20a%20web%20browser%20with%20dozens%20of%20tabs%20open%20and%20occasionally%20using%20photo%20editing%20software%2C%20tasks%20that%20are%20no%20problem%20for%20a%20notebook%20like%20the%20XPS%2013.%20It%20was%20able%20to%20export%20a%2015%2C000%20x%2012%2C000%20image%20file%20in%20a%20little%20more%20than%2010%20seconds%20in%20Adobe%20Photoshop%20Lightroom%2C%20making%20it%20a%20hair%20faster%20than%20the%20M1-powered%20MacBook%20Air%20with%208GB%20of%20RAM%20and%20considerably%20speedier%20than%20the%20older%20XPS%2013%20powered%20by%20Intel's%2010th-generation%20chip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fans%20did%20become%20audible%20when%20using%20the%20Google%20Chrome%20browser%20with%20more%20than%2020%20tabs%20open%2C%20downloading%20a%20large%20video%20game%20from%20Steam%2C%20and%20running%20Adobe%20Lightroom%20all%20at%20once.%20But%20they%20never%20got%20close%20to%20feeling%20overwhelmingly%20loud%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20slowdown%20in%20the%20system's%20performance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dell%20XPS%2013%20performed%20about%20average%20on%20benchmarking%20tests%2C%20with%20results%20that%20were%20nearly%20the%20same%20as%20those%20from%20the%20HP%20Envy%2013%20and%20higher%20than%20the%20previous-generation%20Dell%20XPS%2013's.%20But%20its%20performance%20was%20still%20noticeably%20behind%20the%20M1%20MacBook%20Air%20in%20this%20regard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20running%20a%20program%20called%20Geekbench%205%2C%20which%20measures%20processor%20performance%20by%20simulating%20every%20tasks%2C%20the%20XPS%2013%20scored%204%2C307%20on%20a%20test%20designed%20to%20evaluate%20multi-core%20performance%20and%201%2C279%20on%20the%20single-core%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20HP%20Envy%2013%20scored%204%2C099%20and%201%2C352%20on%20the%20same%20respective%20tests%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techradar.com%2Freviews%2Fhp-envy-13-2020%5C%22%3ETechRadar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Apple's%20M1%20MacBook%20Air%20hit%207%2C558%20and%201%2C726%20in%20my%20own%20experience.%20The%20previous%20generation%20Dell%20XPS%2013%20with%20Intel's%2010th-generation%20processor%20scored%203%2C704%20and%20953%20during%20the%20same%20test%2C%20indicating%20the%20new%20model%20indeed%20comes%20with%20a%20bump%20in%20speed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20bigger%20improvement%20compared%20to%20the%2010th-generation%20variant%20is%20in%20its%20graphics%20performance.%20The%20Core%20i7%20variant%20of%20the%20new%20Dell%20XPS%2013%20comes%20with%20Intel's%20more%20powerful%20Iris%20Xe%20graphics%20while%20the%20last%20model%20includes%20Intel%20UHD%20graphics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20able%20to%20comfortably%20play%20The%20Witcher%203%3A%20Wild%20Hunt%20on%20the%20medium%20graphics%20settings%20at%20a%20resolution%20of%201%2C280%20x%20960%20on%20the%20new%20XPS%2013.%20Performance%20wasn't%20ideal%2C%20but%20it%20was%20reliable%20enough%20to%20play%20the%20game.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20game%20felt%20barely%20playable%20on%20these%20settings%20on%20the%20old%20XPS%2013%20with%2010th-generation%20Intel.%20The%20Dell%20XPS%2013%20isn't%20meant%20for%20gaming%2C%20but%20the%20difference%20still%20illustrates%20the%20big%20step%20forward%20in%20graphics%20performance%20you%20can%20expect%20from%20the%20new%20version.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20the%20version%20of%20this%20configuration%20that%20Dell%20currently%20sells%20is%20actually%20a%20bit%20faster%20than%20the%20one%20I've%20been%20testing%20because%20it%20has%20a%20Core%20i7%20chip%20with%20a%20higher%20boost%20speed.%20Overall%20performance%20should%20generally%20be%20very%20similar%20to%20what%20I've%20experienced%2C%20but%20the%20edition%20Dell%20sells%20might%20be%20faster%20in%20some%20circumstances%20under%20heavy%20workloads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeyboard%20and%20touchpad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dell%20XPS%2013%20Keyboard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fd7e8622069f400194c7b97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Eadicicco%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20keyboard%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20aspects%20of%20a%20laptop%2C%20and%20thankfully%20Dell's%20delivers.%20The%20Dell%20XPS%2013's%20keyboard%20cons