0can%20always%20vary%20depending%20on%20how%20you%20use%20your%20laptop%2C%20so%20your%20results%20may%20not%20match%20mine%20exactly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20only%20one%20complaint%20I%20have%20with%20the%20Dell%20XPS%2013%3A%20its%20webcam%20quality.%20The%20720p%20camera%20produced%20images%20that%20looked%20blurry%20and%20dim%2C%20perhaps%20making%20this%20laptop%20less%20ideal%20for%20video%20calls.%20Compared%20to%20a%202019%20Intel-powered%20MacBook%20Pro%2C%20which%20also%20has%20a%20720p%20webcam%2C%20the%20scene%20looked%20more%20bland%20and%20a%20bit%20fuzzier%20on%20the%20XPS%2013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20find%20a%20laptop%20with%20a%20sharp%20webcam%2C%20and%20720p%20is%20a%20pretty%20standard%20resolution%20for%20the%20camera%20that%20comes%20built%20into%20your%20computer.%20But%20since%20most%20people%20are%20working%20from%20home%20and%20likely%20will%20be%20for%20some%20time%2C%20webcam%20quality%20has%20become%20more%20important%20than%20ever.%20After%20using%20Apple's%20M1%20MacBook%20Pro%2C%20which%20incorporates%20Apple's%20image%20signal%20processor%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20go%20back%20to%20another%20laptop%20without%20this%20advantage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20a%20look%20at%20the%20images%20below%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20the%20Dell%20XPS%2013%20compares%20against%20the%20M1%20MacBook%20Air%20in%20terms%20of%20camera%20quality.%20The%20one%20taken%20on%20Apple's%20computer%20isn't%20perfect%20either%2C%20but%20it%20is%20brighter%20and%20crisper%20than%20the%20image%20taken%20on%20the%20XPS%2013.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDell%20XPS%2013%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dell%20XPS%2013%20Webcam%20Sample%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fd7e93f78a5740019a1567c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Eadicicco%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EApple%20MacBook%20Air%20(M1)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22MacBook%20Air%20M1%20Webcam%20Sample%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fd7e9562069f400194c7ba2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Eadicicco%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20buy%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20the%20Dell%20XPS%2013%20is%20an%20all-around%20top%20choice%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20lightweight%2C%20ultraportable%20laptops.%20If%20you%20need%20a%20laptop%20for%20tasks%20like%20writing%20papers%2C%20browsing%20the%20web%2C%20managing%20spreadsheets%2C%20and%20watching%20Netflix%2C%20the%20Dell%20XPS%2013%20should%20have%20everything%20you%20need.%20The%20webcam%20isn't%20anything%20to%20write%20home%20about%2C%20but%20neither%20are%20the%20ones%20on%20most%20laptops.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20Dell%20XPS%2013%20has%20the%20right%20combination%20of%20performance%20and%20elegance%20to%20satisfy%20most%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20Windows%20fan%20seeking%20a%20compact%2013-inch%20laptop%20for%20everyday%20work%2C%20it's%20also%20worth%20considering%20the%20well-reviewed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstore.hp.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fpdp%2Fhp-envy-laptop-13-ba1097nr%5C%22%3EHP%20Envy%2013%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20similarly%20priced%2C%20with%20a%20configuration%20that%20comes%20with%20an%2011th-generation%20Intel%20Core%20i7%20and%2016GB%20of%20RAM%20but%20less%20storage%20(256GB)%20currently%20selling%20for%20%24899.99.%20It%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20few%20extras%20not%20found%20on%20Dell's%20system%20like%20a%20two%20legacy%20USB%20Type-A%20ports%20and%20a%20camera%20shutter%20for%20priva