C%20and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20bears%20the%20highest%20health%20burden%20attributable%20to%20particulate%20pollution%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20mentioned%20that%20the%20Northern%20Plains%20of%20India%20are%20synonymous%20with%20North%20India%2C%20Northern%20India%2C%20and%20the%20North%20Indian%20Belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faqli.epic.uchicago.edu%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FAQLI_2023_Report-Global_Embargoed.pdf%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98AQLI%202023%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20written%20by%20Michael%20Greenstone%20and%20Christa%20Hasenkopf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFine%20particulate%20air%20pollution%2C%20known%20as%20PM2.5%2C%20has%20been%20found%20to%20reduce%20the%20average%20life%20expectancy%20of%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20by%205.3%20years%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%E2%80%99s%20(WHO)%20recommended%20guideline%20of%205%20%C2%B5g%2Fm3.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20North%20India%2C%20this%20particulate%20pollution%20is%20even%20more%20severe%2C%20cutting%20lives%20short%20by%20eight%20years%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20the%20Northern%20Plains%2C%20which%20is%20home%20to%20a%20population%20of%20521.2%20million%20people%2C%20or%2038.9%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20population%2C%20reside%20in%20areas%20where%20the%20annual%20average%20particulate%20pollution%20levels%20are%2017.3%20times%20higher%20than%20the%20WHO%20guideline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShockingly%2C%20from%201998%20to%202021%2C%20the%20average%20annual%20particulate%20pollution%20has%20surged%20by%2061%25%2C%20further%20diminishing%20life%20expectancy%20by%203.2%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20most%20polluted%20region%20of%20the%20Northern%20Plains%2C%20namely%20the%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%2C%20its%2018%20million%20inhabitants%20are%20facing%20a%20potential%20loss%20of%2011.9%20years%20of%20life%20expectancy%20relative%20to%20the%20WHO%20guideline%2C%20and%208.5%20years%20relative%20to%20the%20national%20guideline%2C%20should%20current%20pollution%20levels%20persist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-india-pollution-idUSKCN1QM1FH%5C%22%3Eranks%20as%20the%20most%20polluted%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India%20and%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20following%20Diwali%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Femergency-think-of-urgent-steps-like-2-day-lockdown-sc-tells-centre-on-delhi-air-pollution%5C%22%3Esurge%20in%20cases%20of%20respiratory%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20health%20emergencies%20is%20reported%2C%20largely%20attributed%20to%20the%20significant%20increase%20in%20pollution%20resulting%20from%20the%20burning%20of%20firecrackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20causes%20of%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-46138064%5C%22%3Ecan%20be%20attributed%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20burning%20of%20farm%20stubble%20in%20neighbouring%20states%2C%20industrial%20emissions%2C%20pollution%20from%20vehicles%2C%20and%20seasonal%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Chicago%20report%20further%20pointed%20out%20that%20even%20in%20the%20least%20contaminated%20district%20within%20the%20region%2C%20Pathankot%2C%20which%20is%20in%20Punjab%2C%20particulate%20pollution%20levels%20exceed%20the%20WHO%20guideline%20by%20more%20than%20sevenfold%2C%20thereby%20shortening%20life%20expectancy%20by%203.1%20years%20if%20current%20levels%20persist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20India%20initiated%20the%20National%20Clean%20Air%20Programme%20(NCAP)%20as%20part%20of%20its%20%E2%80%9Cwar%20against%20pollution%E2%80%9D.%20Initially%2C%20NCAP%20aimed%20to%20decrease%20particulate%20pollution%20by%2020-30%25%20nationwide%20by%202024%2C%20focusing%20on%20102%20cities%20failing%20to%20meet%20India%E2%80%99s%20PM2.5%20standards.%20However%2C%20in%202022%2C%20the%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fnational-clean-air-programme-centre-aims-at-40-reduction-in-particulate-matter-by-2026%2Farticle65941247.ece%5C%22%3Erevised%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20pollution%20reduction%20target%20under%20NCAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20didn%E2%80%99t%20set%20a%20national%20goal%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20it%20set%20an%20ambitious%20city-level%20target%20of%20a%2040%25%20reduction%20by%202025-26%20for%20an%20expanded%20list%20of%20131%20non-attainment%20cities%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAchieving%20this%20target%20would%20lead%20to%20a%2021.9%20%C2%B5g%2Fm%C2%B3%20reduction%20in%20annual%20average%20PM2.5%20exposure%20relative%20to%202017%20levels%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%202.1-year%20increase%20in%20life%20expectancy%20for%20citizens%20in%20these%20131%20cities%2C%20and%20a%207.9-month%20increase%20for%20the%20average%20Indian%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%5BAt%20least%5D%2038%20of%20these%20131%20targeted%20cities%20(almost%2030%25)%20belong%20to%20the%20Northern%20Plains%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693398546000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F01140646%2F2019_10img31_Oct_2019_PTI10_31_2019_000257B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fworld-most-polluted-regions-north-india-delhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fine%20particulate%20air%20pollution%20lowers%20the%20average%20life%20expectancy%20of%20an%20Indian%20by%205.3%20years.%20In%20North%20India%2C%20this%20pollution%20is%20even%20more%20severe%2C%20reducing%20life%20expectancy%20by%20eight%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fworld-most-polluted-regions-north-india-delhi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G20%20Summit%20traffic%20advisory%3A%20Check%20what%20routes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693398492000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103215310%2Cimgsize-1440864.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fnews%2Fg20-summit-traffic-advisory-check-what-routes-to-avoid-between-7-10-sept%2Farticleshow%2F103213919.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%20recently%20issued%20a%20revised%20traffic%20advisory%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit%202023%2C%20slated%20between%209-10%20September%202023.%20The%20new%20advisory%20will%20ensure%20hassle-free%20movement%20of%20vehicles%20within%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20District%20and%20its%20surrounding%20areas.%20According%20to%20the%20advisory%2C%20general%20traffic%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20Delhi%20from%20the%20Rajokari%20Border%2C%20except%20buses%20and%20goods%20vehicles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fnews%2Fg20-summit-traffic-advisory-check-what-routes-to-avoid-between-7-10-sept%2Farticleshow%2F103213919.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20is%20fielding%20new%20%243%2C500%20'cardboard'%20drones%20against%20Russia%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20flat-packed%20and%20could%20prove%20deadly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20constructed%20SYPAQ%20Corvo%20PPDS%20drone%2C%20sitting%20atop%20a%20stack%20of%20flat-packed%20ones.%20Two%20arrows%20point%20to%20both%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bbuilt%20drone%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3B12%20more%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ef2d1bbdd7e70019dfd0d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20constructed%20SYPAQ%20Corvo%20PPDS%20drone%2C%20sitting%20atop%20a%20stack%20of%20flat-packed%20ones.%3Cp%3ESYPAQ%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUkraine%20has%20received%20hundreds%20of%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bcardboard%20drones%26quot%3B%20from%20Australia.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Corvo%20PPDS%20is%20cheap%2C%20comes%20flat-packed%2C%20and%20can%20be%20built%20in%20an%20hour%2C%20its%20maker%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt's%20designed%20for%20reconnaissance%20and%20delivery%2C%20but%20may%20have%20been%20used%20to%20attack%20too.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20low-cost%20%26quot%3Bcardboard%26quot%3B%20drone%20that%20arrives%20flatpacked%20and%20is%20held%20together%20with%20rubber%20bands%20is%20giving%20Ukraine%20an%20unexpected%20edge%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20called%20the%20Corvo%20Precision%20Payload%20Delivery%20System%2C%20or%20PPDS%20for%20short%2C%20and%20is%20made%20by%20the%20Australian%20company%20SYPAQ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20in%20Ukrainian%20hands%20since%20March%2C%20when%20the%20Australian%20government%20announced%20it%20would%20send%20at%20least%20100%20per%20month%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%2420%20million%20aid%20package%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theaustralian.com.au%2Fnation%2Fcheap-australian-drones-made-of-cardboard-helping-ukrainian-troops%2Fnews-story%2F72e4913bc4f34c2b3fbfc8921fc2bc58%3Famp%26nk%3D99754c0dbc039dbcb7924d82bb8a25b4-1679402875%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Australian%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorvouas.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FCORVO-PPDS-web-version-23082023-compressed.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20SYPAQ%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20drone%20arrives%20in%20a%20package%20some%20two%20and%20a%20half%20feet%20long%20%E2%80%94%20and%20isn't%20much%20more%20complicated%20than%20an%20IKEA%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20low-tech%20framework%20is%20packed%20with%20a%20military-grade%20guidance%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESYPAQ%20says%20it's%20quick%20to%20assemble%20the%20drone%20from%20its%20parts%3A%20a%20lightweight%20board%20frame%2C%20a%20propeller%20unit%2C%20and%20an%20avionics%20system%20which%20soldiers%20can%20program%20with%20a%20target%20location.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drone%20can%20carry%20up%20to%206.6%20pounds%2C%20making%20it%20useful%20for%20dropping%20off%20medicines%20or%20ammunition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20adapt%20it%20for%20reconnaissance%2C%20soldiers%20simply%20%26quot%3Bcut%20a%20hole%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20drone%20for%20a%20camera%20to%20see%20through%2C%20SYPAQ%20manager%20Michael%20Partridge%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theregister.com%2F2023%2F04%2F07%2Fcorvo_cardboard_drone%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20IT-focused%20news%20outlet%20The%20Register%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20finished%20build%20has%20a%20wingspan%20of%20around%20six%20and%20a%20half%20feet.%20It%20is%20so%20light%20it%20can%20be%20launched%20by%20catapult%2C%20or%20literally%20by%20being%20thrown%20like%20a%20giant%20paper%20plane%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-k-2W23s3Ys%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Australia's%207News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20reported%20cost%20of%20around%20%243%2C500%20each%2C%20they're%20cheap%20by%20military%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20drone%2C%20made%20from%20a%20lightweight%20material%20that%20resembles%20carboard%2C%20in%20the%20air%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64edd1b59664cf0019e7f3a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESYPAQ's%20Corvo%20PPDS%20drone.%3Cp%3ESYPAQ%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20its%20payload%2C%20it%20travels%20at%20around%2037%20miles%20per%20hour%2C%20and%20has%20a%20range%20of%20up%20to%2075%20miles.%20And%20when%20it%20arrives%2C%20soldiers%20can%20simply%20retrieve%20the%20cargo%2C%20detach%20the%20propeller%20and%20avionics%20module%2C%20and%20throw%20away%20the%20frame.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it's%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bcardboard%20drone%2C%26quot%3B%20there's%20conflicting%20information%20as%20to%20what%20its%20main%20framework%20is%20actually%20made%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPartridge%20told%20The%20Register%20that%20it's%20made%20of%20waxed%20cardboard%20%E2%80%94%20a%20description%20repeated%20in%20nearly%20all%20media%20reporting%20so%20far.%20In%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sypaq.com.au%2Fnews%2Fsypaq-supporting-ukrainian-armed-forces%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20recent%20announcement%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%20coyly%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bknown%20as%20the%20'cardboard%20plane.'%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorvouas.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FCORVO-PPDS-web-version-23082023-compressed.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBut%20a%20product%20specification%3C%2Fa%3E%20uploaded%20on%20the%20company's%20website%2C%20likely%20in%20late%20August%2C%20describes%20it%20as%20being%20made%20from%20lightweight%20foldable%20foam%20board%2C%20which%20appears%20to%20match%20some%20images.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESYPAQ%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20clarification%2C%20sent%20outside%20of%20working%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECardboard%20is%20%26quot%3Btransparent%20to%20radar%2C%20so%20harder%20to%20spot%2C%26quot%3B%20Oklahoma%20State%20University%20drone%20researcher%20Jamey%20Jacob%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.popularmechanics.com%2Fmilitary%2Faviation%2Fa43432035%2Fukraine-cardboard-drones-stealth%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Popular%20Mechanics%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20radar%20will%20pick%20up%20things%20such%20as%20electric%20motors%2C%20batteries%2C%20and%20propellers%2C%20but%20not%20the%20cardboard%2C%26quot%3B%20Jacob%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20potential%20capacity%20for%20extra%20stealth%20gained%20media%20attention%20this%20week%20when%20Ukraine's%20ambassador%20to%20Australia%20echoed%20claims%20by%20a%20prominent%20Russian%20military%20blogger%20that%20they%20were%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-says-struck-5-russian-jets-drones-made-cardboard-2023-8%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3Eto%20attack%20a%20Russian%20airfield%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20details%20of%20the%20attack%20remain%20unconfirmed%20%E2%80%94%20including%20whether%20Corvo%20PPDSs%20were%20even%20involved%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20airfield%20was%20just%20within%20the%20drone's%20reach%20from%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20the%20%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffighter_bomber%2F13797%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22baae9012cbbf1630112c5f7e41fa46e3%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffighter_bomber%2F13797%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epro-Russian%20Telegram%20channel%20%40fighter_bomber%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ukraine%20used%20a%20swarm-like%20formation%20of%20several%20unarmed%20Corvo%20PPDSs%20amidst%20drones%20packed%20with%20bombs%2C%20helping%20the%20swarm%20evade%20radar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutlining%20another%20potentially%20destructive%20use%20of%20the%20drone%2C%20the%20former%20Australian%20general%20Mick%20Ryan%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theage.com.au%2Fpolitics%2Ffederal%2Faussie-cardboard-drones-used-in-attack-on-russian-airfield-20230829-p5e0bv.html%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%2290f627f7fce547519ce9c643edda193a%5C%22%20data-an