T%2C%20an%20organisation%20that%20works%20for%20the%20upliftment%20of%20women%20and%20children%20%E2%80%94%20says%20that%20water%20scarcity%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20of%20the%20city%2C%20and%20flooding%20during%20monsoons%20has%20now%20become%20extremely%20common.%20%E2%80%9CUrbanisation%20has%20impacted%20natural%20biodiversity%2C%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20forests%20and%20hills%20being%20cut%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20rising%20fluctuations%20and%20climatic%20changes%20affect%20low-income%20groups%20due%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20socio-economic%20and%20demographic%20factors.%20During%20the%202005%20Mumbai%20floods%2C%20over%20a%20million%20slum%20residents%20were%20stranded.%20These%20are%20the%20neighbourhoods%20that%20often%20lack%20access%20to%20basic%20services%20and%20amenities%20like%20potable%20water%2C%20energy%2C%20sanitation.%20For%20instance%2C%2084.9%25%20of%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20M-East%20ward%20population%20lives%20in%20slums%2C%20and%20only%2053.6%25%20of%20these%20households%20have%20access%20to%20water%20on%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdharavi-1693381664.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdharavi-1693381664.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdharavi-1693381664-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdharavi-1693381664-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdharavi-1693381664-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdharavi-1693381664-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image