n%3EThe%20atmospherics%20are%2C%20on%20the%20whole%2C%20positive%20though%20these%20could%20have%20been%20better.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20basic%20question%20too%3A%20Can%20all%20the%20parties%20of%20the%20conglomerate-in-the-making%20resist%20the%20high-scale%20coercion%20the%20establishment%20can%20bring%20on%2C%20and%20stick%20it%20out%20to%20the%20end%3F%20Maharashtra%20affairs%20are%20worth%20watching%20in%20this%20context%2C%20but%20also%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20can%20some%20regional%20leaders%20resist%20personal%20ambitions%20and%20not%20fight%20two%20battles%20simultaneously%20%E2%80%93%20one%20to%20defeat%20the%20quasi-dictatorship%2C%20and%20two%20to%20promote%20their%20personal%20or%20party%20interests%3F%20They%20probably%20can%2C%20though%20it%20is%20best%20to%20be%20doubly%20sure.%20But%20if%20they%20fluff%20this%20one%2C%20they%20sink%20together.%20Swimming%20separately%20is%20out%20of%20the%20question.%20The%20regime%20would%20ensure%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20six%20months%20ago%2C%20prominent%20opposition%20leaders%20now%20in%20the%20INDIA%20formation%20were%20advancing%2C%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20context%2C%20the%20jaded%20and%20bizarre%20formula%20of%20striking%20out%20on%20an%20anti-BJP%2C%20anti-Congress%20path%2C%20self-servingly%20asserting%20that%20there%20was%20no%20difference%20between%20these%20parties.%20Such%20nonsense%20had%20no%20takers%20among%20the%20people%20and%20everyone%20made%20fun%20of%20the%20stunt%20growing%20out%20of%20the%20south%20and%20the%20east.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-opposition-has-discovered-that-modi-is-jaded-and-faded%5C%22%3EThe%20Opposition%20Has%20Discovered%20That%20Modi%20Is%20Jaded%20and%20Faded%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20once%20INDIA%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-opposition-parties-meet-in-bengaluru-here-are-the-9-big-factors-at-play%5C%22%3Eborn%20in%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20an%20immaculate%20conception%20in%20Patna%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20playing%20a%20centripetal%20hand%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20began%20to%20fulminate%2C%20and%20then%20wilt.%20The%20wilting%20was%20on%20pathetic%20display%20in%20his%20reply%20to%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20debate%20in%20parliament%20and%20his%20ritualistic%20address%20from%20Red%20Fort%20on%20Independence%20Day%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20popular%20perception%2C%20there%20was%20now%20at%20last%20the%20plausibility%20of%20resistance.%20The%20opposition%20parties%2C%20if%20they%20held%20fast%2C%20could%20challenge%20a%20regime%20that%20had%20become%20openly%20defiant%20of%20public%20opinion%2C%20openly%20oppressive%2C%20unrepentantly%20given%20to%20inflicting%20violence%20upon%20the%20people%2C%20and%20wantonly%20suppressing%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20farmers%20in%20order%20to%20exalt%20the%20richest%20of%20the%20rich%20classes%2C%20and%20to%20jail%20those%20who%20dissented%20and%20protested.%20In%20fact%2C%20this%20is%20the%20moment%20when%20Modi%20slipped%20from%20the%20pedestal.%20The%20parallelogram%20of%20forces%20began%20to%20change%20direction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20change%20is%20still%20on%20the%20path%20to%20full%20realisation%20and%20will%20probably%20find%20its%20crystallised%20form%20after%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20Mumbai%20confabulation.%20Nevertheless%2C%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%20the%20present%20conjuncture%20beckoned%20the%20rampaging%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20declare%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20during%20the%20recent%20no-confidence%20motion%20debate%20that%2C%20exactly%20like%20the%20demon-king%20Ravana%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20too%20heeds%20the%20advice%20of%20just%20two%20people%20%E2%80%93%20his%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20and%20the%20tycoon%20Gautam%20Adani.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20reality%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20just%20one%20man%E2%80%99s%20voice%20counts.%20The%20indications%20are%20that%20Adani%20and%20Modi%20are%20peas%20in%20a%20pod.%20Reportedly%2C%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20doled%20out%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fgujarat-govt-paid-rs-3-900-cr-of-excess-payment-to-adani-power-gohil-123082600845_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earound%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore%20to%20an%20Adani%20enterprise%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ewithout%20bills%20being%20presented.%20Coincidence%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20connection%2C%20Gujarat%20Congress%20president%20Shaktisinh%20Gohil%20has%20reportedly%20produced%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20Gujarat%20Urja%20Vikas%20Nigam%20Ltd%20to%20Adani%20Power%2C%20Mundra%2C%20in%20which%20the%20state%20power%20utility%20says%20it%20made%20an%20%E2%80%9Cexcess%20payment%E2%80%9D%20of%20Rs%203%2C900%20crore%20to%20Adani%20Power%20between%202018%20and%202023.%20This%20begs%20the%20question%3A%20Is%20this%20an%20example%20of%20poor%20accounting%20by%20a%20government%20enterprise%2C%20or%20political%20largesse%20%E2%80%93%20in%20effect%2C%20the%20Modi%20effect%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F669744%2Fadanis-acquisitions-india-needs-to-keep-track-costs%2F%5C%22%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20Acquisitions%3A%20Why%20India%20Needs%20to%20Keep%20Track%20of%20the%20Costs%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20Shah%2C%20he%20is%20doubtless%2C%20clever%2C%20devious%2C%20energetic%20and%20a%20long-time%20lieuten