asury%20benches%20rose%20to%20challenge%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20scathing%20assertions%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20A%20late%20retort%20came%20from%20Union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20who%20remained%20unmoved%20when%20a%20rape%20video%20surfaced%20from%20Manipur.%20As%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20leaving%20the%20House%2C%20in%20a%20revenge%20attack%2C%20she%20accused%20him%20of%20blowing%20a%20flying%20kiss%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20women%20on%20the%20treasury%20benches%20and%20complained%20to%20the%20Speaker!%20In%20effect%2C%20Modi%20was%20left%20to%20fend%20for%20himself%20by%20his%20party.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-narendra-modi-nervous%5C%22%3EHas%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%20Made%20PM%20Modi%20Nervous%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20has%20attacked%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%20in%20season%20and%20out%20of%20season%2C%20in%20Parliament%20and%20outside.%20Distinctly%20feeling%20cornered%20when%20addressing%20the%20nation%20from%20the%20Red%20Fort%20on%20Independence%20Day%2C%20he%20literally%20begged%20the%20people%20for%20%E2%80%9Chelp%E2%80%9D%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20vote%20for%20a%20single%20party%20(rather%20than%20an%20alliance).%20No%20other%20prime%20minister%20has%20used%20the%20Red%20Fort%20gathering%20on%20August%2015%20as%20an%20election%20rally%20before%2C%20but%20Modi%20is%20not%20above%20setting%20a%20dubious%20record.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20the%20birth%20of%20INDIA%2C%20the%20very%20notion%20of%20an%20opposition%20to%20Modi%20was%20reassuringly%20entertaining%20at%20best.%20With%20INDIA%20coming%20into%20play%2C%20everything%20began%20to%20look%20probable.%20The%20emergence%20of%20an%20opposition-for-itself%2C%20in%20short%20an%20opposition%20for%20the%20people%20in%20their%20dire%20hour%2C%20has%20now%20developed%20recognisable%20contours.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Gramsci%E2%80%99s%20famous%20postulation%20of%20%E2%80%9Cwar%20of%20position%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20ideological%20battlefield%20against%20the%20forces%20of%20fascism%2C%20it%20can%20now%20be%20posited%20that%20the%20emerging%20opposition%20bloc%20appears%20to%20have%20forged%20ahead%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20sycophantic%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebhakt%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(BJP-RSS%20supporters)%20battalions%2C%20though%20the%20latter%20are%20never%20going%20to%20be%20short%20on%20fire%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20crunch%20situation%2C%20the%20government%20of%20the%20bhakts%20can%20unleash%20all%20kinds%20of%20resources%2C%20including%20high-octane%20propaganda.%20It%20can%20unleash%20the%20Election%20Commission%20itself%20by%20obliging%20it%20to%20resile%20from%20its%20constitutional%20stance%20of%20democratic%20neutrality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20for%20now%20it%20is%20INDIA%2C%20especially%20its%20Congress%20component%2C%20which%20is%20setting%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20narratives%20and%20agenda.%20The%20so-called%20opinion%20polls%20run%20by%20television%20stations%20and%20others%2C%20and%20their%20laughable%20efforts%20of%20daring%20to%20tell%20India%20about%20her%20own%20political%20mood%20many%20months%20before%20an%20election%2C%20may%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20massive%20exercise%20in%20deception%20%E2%80%93%20a%20command%20performance%20aimed%20at%20snatching%20away%20the%20initiative%20from%20the%20national%20opposition.%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20these%20circumstances%2C%20it%20is%20doubtful%20if%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20play%20up%20a%20point%20of%20national%20glory%2C%20namely%20the%20superb%20success%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20or%20the%20upcoming%20G-20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20can%20be%20notched%20up%20in%20the%20credit%20column%20for%20the%20prime%20minister.%20People%20are%20learning%20to%20watch%20critically.%20They%20would%20instinctively%20know%20that%20what%20is%20practically%20a%20ban%20on%20entering%20Delhi%20and%20on%20free%20movement%20within%20the%20national%20capital%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20the%20summit%2C%20is%20a%20police%20tactic%20to%20head%20off%20any%20possible%20protest.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-g20-summit-closing-down-a-city%5C%22%3EClosing%20Down%20A%20City%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20present%20autocracy%20is%20a%20one-trick%20pony.%20It%20can%20hope%20to%20rally%20its%20forces%20only%20within%20sections%20of%20the%20majority%20religious%20community%20in%20hopes%20of%20maintaining%20hegemony%20on%20a%20communal%20basis%2C%20not%20democratically.%20This%20is%20achieved%20through%20the%20calibrated%20use%20of%20communal%20violence.%20We%20have%20seen%20this%20happen%20with%20focused%20intent%20since%20important%20state%20polls%20and%20the%20national%20elections%20are%20near.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlas%2C%20this%20is%20what%20India%20has%20been%20reduced%20to.%20The%20technique%20has%20been%20on%20display%20for%20more%20than%20three%20months%20in%20Manipur%2C%20where%20violence%20continues%20to%20be%20produced%20on%20the%20political%20assembly-line%2C%20or%20the%20chief%20minister%20would%20have%20been%20sent%20packing%20long%20ago.%20Instead%2C%20the%20man%20is%20cosseted%20by%20the%20Centre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Nuh%2C%20in%20Haryana%2C%20the%20communal%20violence%2C%20%3Ca%2