20its%20glorification%2C%20is%20woven%20into%20the%20very%20fabric%20of%20a%20communally-driven%20regime.%20This%20is%20writ%20large%20into%20the%20script%20of%20a%20government%20which%2C%20by%20its%20very%20nature%2C%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20even-handed%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20what%20the%20rule-book%20says%3B%20indeed%20its%20aim%20is%20to%20replace%20the%20rule%20book%20in%20the%20fashion%20of%20the%20Nazis%2C%20or%20in%20emulation%20of%20the%20Zionists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20a%20dispensation%2C%20in%20hopes%20of%20not%20getting%20burnt%2C%20seeks%20to%20rely%20on%20hate%20propaganda%20and%20communal%20consolidation%20in%20order%20to%20come%20back%20electorally.%20The%20trick%20has%20worked%20for%20nine%20years%20principally%20because%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20media%20has%20capitulated.%20It%20has%20been%20subverted%20in%20more%20ways%20than%20one%2C%20and%20calculatedly%20fails%20to%20show%20the%20government%20the%20mirror%20in%20order%20to%20benefit%20those%20who%20seek%20to%20lay%20the%20path%20to%20fascism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20crushed%20under%20financial%2C%20emotional%2C%20psychological%20and%20communal%20burdens%2C%20the%20people%20are%2C%20at%20last%2C%20catching%20on.%20The%20regime%20has%20also%20grown%20increasingly%20aware%20of%20the%20bush%20fires%20burning%20within.%20That%20makes%20it%20extra%20jumpy.%20It%20has%20begun%20to%20see%20ghosts%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eeverywhere.%20That%20is%20why%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20Congress%20party%20or%20the%20INDIA%20combine%20that%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20seeks%20to%20suppress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20Nitin%20Gadkari%E2%80%99s%20case%20stands%20out.%20The%20Union%20minister%20in%20charge%20of%20building%20national%20highways%20and%20ports%2C%20who%20has%20en