A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fasia-cup%2Fpakistan-need-to-expose-virat-kohli-early-former-australia-spinner-brad-hogg-on-asia-cup-clash%2Farticleshow%2F103213771.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Australian%20leg-spinner%20and%20World%20Cup%20winner%20Brad%20Hogg%20feels%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20highly%20anticipated%20clash%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20hinges%20on%20the%20battle%20between%20Shaheen%20Afridi%20and%20the%20Indian%20top-order%20batters.%20And%20if%20Pakistan%20want%20to%20get%20on%20top%20of%20the%20game%2C%20they%20need%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20star%20Indian%20batter%20Virat%20Kohli%20early%20in%20the%20contest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fasia-cup%2Fpakistan-need-to-expose-virat-kohli-early-former-australia-spinner-brad-hogg-on-asia-cup-clash%2Farticleshow%2F103213771.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Should%20Tie%20Rakhi%20To%20Bilkis%20Bano%2C%20Wrestlers%3A%20Opposition%20Ahead%20Of%20Meet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Common%20Minimum%20Programme%20and%20a%20dialogue%20about%20seat%20sharing%20may%20figure%20in%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20third%20meeting%20of%20the%20united%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%2C%20its%20leaders%20have%20indicated%20ahead%20of%20the%20two-day%20meet%20that%20begins%20in%20Mumbai%20tomorrow.%2028%20parties%20will%20take%20part%20in%20the%20meet%20--%20two%20more%20than%20the%20last%20one%20in%20Bengaluru%20--%20along%20with%20six%20Chief%20Ministers%20of%20Opposition-ruled%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20be%20sitting%20and%20discussing%20a%20Common%20Minimum%20Programme%2C%26quot%3B%20veteran%20leader%20Sharad%20Pawar%20told%20reporters%20this%20evening.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWe%20have%20yet%20to%20start%20the%20dialogue%20for%20seat%20sharing.%20There%20is%20a%20chance%20that%20we