for%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20called%20the%20name%20pretentious%20and%20pitched%20the%20concept%20of%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20against%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20people%20are%20seeing%20who%20all%20are%20a%20part%20of%20NDA.%20They%20work%20for%20the%20shoshit%20and%20vanchit%2C%20adivasis%20and%20peechhdas%20(exploited%20and%20deprived%2C%20tribals%20and%20backward%20communities)...%20It%20is%20dedicated%20to%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693395780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2F76hil6ao_uddhav-thackeray-at-the-dasara-melava-rally_625x300_07_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-should-tie-rakhis-to-bilkis-bano-women-of-manipur-wrestlers-uddhav-thackeray-ahead-of-opposition-bloc-india-meet-4342392%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Common%20Minimum%20Programme%20and%20a%20dialogue%20about%20seat%20sharing%20may%20figure%20in%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20third%20meeting%20of%20the%20united%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%2C%20its%20leaders%20have%20indicated%20ahead%20of%20the%20two-day%20meet%20that%20begins%20in%20Mumbai%20tomorrow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-should-tie-rakhis-to-bilkis-bano-women-of-manipur-wrestlers-uddhav-thackeray-ahead-of-opposition-bloc-india-meet-4342392%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-should-tie-rakhis-to-bilkis-bano-women-of-manipur-wrestlers-uddhav-thackeray-ahead-of-opposition-bloc-india-meet-4342392%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-should-tie-rakhis-to-bilkis-bano-women-of-manipur-wrestlers-uddhav-thackeray-ahead-of-opposition-bloc-india-meet-4342392%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%