ts-dds-ny.un.org%2Fdoc%2FUNDOC%2FGEN%2FG20%2F232%2F15%2FPDF%2FG2023215.pdf%3FOpenElement%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EInternational%20Covenant%20on%20Civil%20and%20Political%20Rights%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20finds%20in%20the%20rights%20to%20associate%20and%20assemble%20the%20fundamental%20political%20right%20which%20is%20essential%20for%20all%20people%20%E2%80%9Cin%20shaping%20their%20societies%E2%80%9D.%20These%20rights%20constitute%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20very%20foundation%20of%20a%20system%20of%20participatory%20governance%20based%20on%20democracy%2C%20human%20rights%2C%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20pluralism.%E2%80%9D%20Article%2020%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fsites%2Fun2.un.org%2Ffiles%2F2021%2F03%2Fudhr.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUniversal%20Declaration%20of%20Human%20Rights%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20states%20that%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20has%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20peaceful%20assembly%20and%20association%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20may%20be%20compelled%20to%20belong%20to%20an%20association%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Indian%20constitution%20under%20Article%2019(1)%20(c)%20guarantees%20freedom%20of%20%E2%80%9Cassociation%20or%20unions%E2%80%9D%20with%20a%20few%20restrictions%20which%20are%20public%20order%2C%20decency%2C%20and%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20India.%20We%20should%20note%20that%20it%20is%20the%20people%20who%20are%20%E2%80%98sovereign%E2%80%99%20and%20that%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdistricts.ecourts.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Ffctwrkshop.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20judicial%20decision%20or%20order%20which%20violates%20a%20fundamental%20right%20is%20void%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFreedom%20of%20association%20is%20most%20commonly%20the%20freedom%2C%20and%20the%20power%2C%20to%20form%20organisations%20including%20political%20parties.%20Freedom%20of%20association%20is%20also%20the%20power%20that%20grounds%20our%20freedom%20to%20love%2C%20to%20create%20languages%2C%20to%20marry%2C%20to%20educate%20each%20other%2C%20to%20convert%20to%20religions%20and%20to%20form%20communes%20among%20friends.%20Caste%20order%20is%20explicitly%20opposed%20to%20freedom%20of%20association%20and%20it%20has%20been%20subverting%20the%20constitution.%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20gave%20the%20clearest%20explanation%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAnnihilation%20of%20Caste%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20your%20ideal%20society%20if%20you%20do%20not%20want%20caste%20is%20a%20question%20that%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20asked%20of%20you.%20If%20you%20ask%20me%2C%20my%20ideal%20would%20be%20a%20society%20based%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3ELiberty%2C%20Equality%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EFraternity%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20why%20not%3F%20What%20objection%20can%20there%20be%20to%20Fraternity%3F%20I%20cannot%20imagine%20any.%20An%20ideal%20society%20should%20be%20mobile%2C%20should%20be%20full%20of%20channels%20for%20conveying%20a%20change%20taking%20place%20in%20one%20part%20to%20other%20parts.%20In%20an%20ideal%20society%20there%20should%20be%20many%20interests%20consciously%20communicated%20and%20shared.%20There%20should%20be%20varied%20and%20free%20points%20of%20contact%20with%20other%20modes%20of%20association.%20In%20other%20words%20there%20must%20be%20social%20endosmosis.%20This%20is%20fraternity%2C%20which%20is%20only%20another%20name%20for%20democracy.%20Democracy%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20form%20of%20Government.%20It%20is%20primarily%20a%20mode%20of%20associated%20living%2C%20of%20conjoint%20communicated%20experience.%20It%20is%20essentially%20an%20attitude%20of%20respect%20and%20reverence%20towards%20fellowmen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECaste%20order%20and%20its%20ethos%20prevents%20the%20people%20of%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20and%20other%20religious%20groups%20(especially%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20of%20those%20groups)%20from%20associating%20with%20one%20another%20through%20love%2C%20living%20in%20shared%20neighbourhoods%2C%20sitting%20at%20the%20same%20table%2C%20studying%20in%20the%20same%20classrooms%2C%20presiding%20on%20judgment%20in%20the%20courts%20of%20India%2C%20in%20the%20parliament%2C%20and%20in%20the%20media.%20There%20are%20new%20laws%2C%20with%20unpronounceable%20Hindi%20names%2C%20which%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Funder-new-bill-marrying-woman-by-concealing-identity-will-invite-10-years-jail-101691808075638-amp.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eopposed%20to%20the%20right%20to%20associate%20freely%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20they%20are%20a%20bad%20omen%20for%20the%20more%20evil%20transformations%20of%20the%20state%20after%20the%202024%20national%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20the%20restrictions%20on%20freedom%20of%20association%20are%20often%20imposed%20by%20the%20media%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emafia%20famiglia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20RSS.%20The%20state%20too%20is%20clearly%20intervening%20in%20the%20domain%20of%20religious%20freedoms%2C%20especially%20the%20freedom%20to%20associate%20with%20any%20religions%20and%20the%20negative%20freedom%20to%20dissociate%20from%20religions.%20This%20is%20a%20subversion%20of%20the%20constitution.%20For%20understanding%20negative%20freedoms%2C%20the%20iconic%20example%20is%20the%20religious%20conversion%20of%20Ambedkar%2C%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20associate%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9CHindu%E2%80%9D%20order%20and%20hence%20chose%20Buddhism%20in%20a%20mass%20religious%20conversion%20event%20on%20October%2014%2C%201956.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcountercurrents.org%2F2022%2F10%2Fwhy-are-the-twenty-two-vows-necessary-for-neo-buddhists%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E22%20vows%20taken%20by%20the%20father%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20that%20mass%20conversion%20event%20say%20much%20about%20the%20conflict%20between%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20and%20upper%20caste%20supremacism%20which%20directs%20itself%20as%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20state.%20We%20must%20recall%20three%20of%20the%20vows%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20believe%20in%20the%20equality%20of%20men.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20will%20try%20to%20establish%20equality.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20renounce%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Freligion%2Fhow-upper-castes-invented-hindu-majority%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHinduism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20is%20harmful%20to%20humanity%20and%20hinders%20the%20progress%20and%20development%20of%20humanity%20because%20it%20is%20based%20on%20inequality%2C%20and%20adopt%20Buddhism%20as%20self-religion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%3C%2Fspan%3E%201%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%3C%2Fspan%3E%202%3Cspan%3E%20are%20consistent%20with%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%2C%20while%203%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20points%20to%20the%20serious%20threat%20posed%20by%20upper%20caste%20supremacism%20to%20the%20constitution%20of%20India.%20These%20threats%20are%20becoming%20more%20alarming%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-atmanirbhar-bharat-rss-hindu-economics-rashtra%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecaste%20order%20is%20surreptitiously%20introduced%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20into%20the%20education%20system%2C%20in%20the%20name%20of%20encouraging%20%E2%80%9Ctraditional%E2%80%9D%20crafts%20and%20jobs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENearly%20all%20religious%20groupings%20and%20many%20political%20parties%20of%20India%20are%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20freedoms%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20as%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20recent%20incidents%20where%20the%20freedoms%20of%20expression%20and%20association%20appeared%20in%20conflict%20with%20religions.%20A%20lower%20caste%20leader%20of%20the%20AAP%20and%20a%20former%20minister%20of%20the%20government%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Rajendra%20Pal%20Gautam%2C%20converted%20to%20Buddhism%20in%20October%202022%20in%20a%20mass%20conversion%20event%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi-news%2Fbjp-slams-aap-over-conversion-oath-minister-hits-back-at-propaganda-101665167118302.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhere%20hundreds%20of%20people%20denounced%20Hinduism%20and%20adopted%20Buddhism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20After%20several%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FDelhi%2Famid-row-over-mass-conversion-aap-minister-gautam-apologises%2Farticle65982444.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elegal%20complaints%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20refusal%20of%20the%20AAP%20leadership%20to%20defend%20him%20amidst%20reports%20that%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi-news%2Fbjp-slams-aap-over-conversion-oath-minister-hits-back-at-propaganda-101665167118302.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20%E2%80%98is%20extremely%20displeased%E2%80%99%20with%20Gautam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20had%20to%20resign%20from%20his%20ministerial%20position.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20real%20restrictions%20to%20freedom%20of%20association%20are%20imposed%20through%20the%20brutality%20of%20mafia%20organisations%20which%20spring%20up%20often%20as%20paramilitary%20wings%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fencyclopediaofmo0000atki%2Fpage%2F264%2Fmode%2F2up%3Fq%3DRSS%2B1947%2Bbanned%26view%3Dtheater%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ean%20organisation%20banned%20thrice%20since%201947%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20operating%20against%20the%20constitution.%20These%20restrictions%20are%20supported%20and%20aided%20by%20the%20police%20and%20other%20state%20institutions%2C%20and%20occasionally%20by%20the%20judiciary%2C%20which%20indicates%20that%20an%20upper%20caste%20supremacist%20%E2%80%98state%20machinery%E2%80%99%20is%20about%20to%20wriggle%20out%20of%20the%20chrysalis%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20all%20kinds%20of%20associations%20that%20are%20being%20challenged%20and%20suppressed%2C%20the%20most%20alarming%20and%20revealing%20suppressions%20are%20of%20the%20associations%20that%20oppose%20the%20caste%20order%20to%20lead%20towards%20a%20society%20assuring%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%2C%20Liberty%20and%20Equality%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20are%20the%20promises%20of%20the%20constitution.%20That%20is%2C%20these%20three%20values%20are%20both%20the%20principles%2C%20understood%20as%20ground%2C%20and%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20telos%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20understood%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethat%20towards%20which%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20all%20the%20activities%20specified%20by%20the%20constitution%20should%20strive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F02124403%2FAmbedkar_addressing_a_conference_at_Ambedkar_Bhawan_Delhi.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22999%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F02124403%2FAmbedkar_addressing_a_conference_at_Ambedkar_Bhawan_Delhi.jpg%20999w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F02124403%2FAmbedkar_addressing_a_conference_at_Ambedkar_Bhawan_Delhi-300x151.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-568000%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22502%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOn%2020%20May%201951%2C%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%20addressed%20a%20conference%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Buddha%20Jayanti%20organised%20at%20Ambedkar%20Bhawan%2C%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%20%E2%80%93%20CC0%201.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWho%20are%20the%20ones%20unable%20to%20associate%20and%20assemble%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%2020%20this%20year%2C%20a%20collection%20of%20organisations%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20met%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Finching-closer-to-a-police-state-we20-summit-organisers-after-police-refuses-permission-on-day-3%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHKS%20Surjeet%20Bhawan%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20The%20We20%E2%80%99s%20declaration%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwgonifis.net%2F2023%2F08%2F20%2Fpeople-and-nature-over-profits-for-a-just-inclusive-transparent-and-equitable-future%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20and%20Nature%20over%20Profits%20for%20a%20Just%2C%20Inclusive%2C%20Transparent%20and%20Equitable%20Future%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20should%20be%20most%20welcome.%20However%2C%20the%20police%20denied%20them%20permission%20to%20gather%20through%20an%20irrational%20statement%E2%80%94%E2%80%9Cnon%20availability%20of%20the%20vital%20information%20pertaining%20to%20the%20gathering%2C%20visitors%20etc.%20which%20is%20needed%20as%20per%20oredor%20(sic)%20of%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20High%20Court%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%A6%5Bpermission%20for%5D%20program%20is%20hereby%20rejected%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202018%2C%20scholars%2C%20activists%2C%20academics%2C%20former%20judges%2C%20and%20people%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%20gathered%20to%20commemorate%20the%20200th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20victory%20of%20a%20lower%20caste%20army%20over%20a%20Brahmin%20kingdom%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Then%20the%20worst%20violations%20of%20human%20rights%2C%20international%20law%2C%20and%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20were%20unleashed%20in%20order%20to%20imprison%20many%20who%20participated%20in%20these%20events%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpms-rural-development-fellows-come-out-in-support-of-mahesh-raut%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esome%20who%20did%20not%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Flaw%2Fdid-pune-police-tamper-evidence-against-bhima-koregaon-accused%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eevidence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fmodified-elephant-planted-evidence-hacking-police%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efound%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20have%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fsecurity-researchers-claim-link-between-pune-police-and-hacking-campaign-against-bhima-koreagon-accused%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eplanted%20on%20the%20computer%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20an%20accused%20and%20the%20statements%20of%20this%20spurious%20evidence%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmany-plots-to-assassinate-narendra-modi%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eludicrous%20and%20juvenile%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20slow%20judicial%20process%20in%20this%20case%20and%20the%20death%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-compassionate-revolution-of-saint-stan-swamy%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFather%20Stan%20Swamy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20prison%20serve%20as%20intimidation%20and%20warning%20to%20all%20those%20who%20seek%20an%20egalitarian%20polity%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20position.%20Those%20who%20speak%2C%20associate%2C%20and%20assemble%20from%20this%20position%20are%20considered%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Brahminical%20minority%20position%2C%20as%20asserted%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fviolence-in-maharashtra-as-dalits-protest-death-of-28-year-old-in-bhima-koregaon-clashes%2Fstory-zerVWqrSjLjF2x53oHMVXL.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAkhil%20Bharatiya%20Brahmin%20Mahasangh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20so%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%2C%20not%20yet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%2C%20negative%20freedom%20of%20association%20may%20appear%20as%20it%20did%20in%20Nazi%20Germany%2C%20everyone%20may%20be%20made%20an%20automatic%20member%20of%20the%20RSS.%20Before%20that%20comes%20about%2C%20we%20should%20breathe%20life%20back%20into%20the%20constitution%20through%20the%20exercise%20of%20the%20rights%20guaranteed%20by%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20fitness%20test%20of%20the%20constitution%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20health%20of%20the%20constitution%20must%20be%20tested%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20in%20the%20halls%20of%20justice%2C%20and%20these%20tests%20are%20the%20responsibility%20of%20everyone%2C%20not%20just%20the%20activists%20and%20lawyers.%20We%20should%20gather%20over%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee%20under%20an%20idea%20whenever%20possible.%20We%20should%20form%20newer%20associations%20in%20the%20mode%20of%20weekend%20clubs%20to%20educate%20one%20another%20about%20the%20political%20history%20of%20India%2C%20mourn%20its%20present%2C%20and%20draft%20its%20future.%20We%20should%20associate%20and%20share%20books%2C%20articles%20and%20other%20resources%20so%20that%20we%20become%20the%20egalitarian%20gathering%20of%20an%20effervescent%20power%20opposing%20an%20evanescent%20force%20composed%20of%20barely%20literate%20goons%20and%20clowns.%20We%20should%20also%20visit%20those%20neighbourhoods%20within%20our%20neighbourhoods%20that%20are%20kept%20apart%20under%20caste%20and%20religious%20apartheid.%20Above%20all%2C%20associate%20in%20the%20greatest%20of%20numbers%20for%20egalitarianism%20as%20such.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20acts%20will%20be%20policed%2C%20mobbed%2C%20and%20terrorised%20with%20the%20connivance%20of%20some%20office%20bearers%20of%20the%20institutions%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20India%20and%20by%20the%20cowards%20who%20walk%20the%20streets%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20terrify%20everyone%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Freligion%2Fhow-upper-castes-invented-hindu-majority%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20recently%20invented%20religion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20RSS%2C%20as%20we%20have%20known%20them%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20anti-colonial%20movement%20and%20since%201947%2C%20are%20cowards%20who%20operate%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20in%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20crowds%20or%2C%20today%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fformer-delhi-police-officer-who-let-kapil-mishra-make-fiery-speech-before-delhi-riots-seeks-medal%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20security%20offered%20by%20high%20ranking%20policemen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20we%20should%20freely%20assemble%20in%20the%20open%20in%20order%20to%20open%20politics%20again%20as%20the%20quest%20for%20freedom%3B%20bearing%20moral%20courage%20and%20the%20creative%20power%20of%20lamentation%20wi