pan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Chistorically%2C%20culturally%20and%20politically%2C%20the%20tradition%20of%20public%20meetings%2C%20processions%2C%20assemblies%20etc.%2C%20on%20streets%2C%20highways%20etc.%2C%20have%20been%20recognized%20in%20this%20country.%20These%20meetings%2C%20processions%20etc.%2C%20constitute%20an%20important%20facet%20of%20our%20political%20life.%20The%20freedom%20struggle%20is%20replete%20with%20examples%20of%20processions%2C%20dharnas%2C%20satyagrahas%20etc.%2C%20conducted%20on%20the%20roads%20which%20lead%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20tryst%20with%20destiny%20on%2015.08.1947.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20constitutional%20court%20acted%20according%20to%20the%20principles%20and%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etelos%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(the%20goals)%20of%20the%20constitution%20and%2C%20against%20the%20trespass%20on%20it%20by%20the%20executive.%20Further%2C%20the%20judgment%20gives%20an%20argument%20for%20the%20rights%20to%20associate%20and%20to%20assemble%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esince%20the%20constitution%20is%20itself%20a%20product%20of%20free%20associations%20and%20assemblies%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20used%20to%20suppress%20these%20rights%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20constitution%20itself%20says%20that%20these%20articles%20of%20freedom%20have%20been%20put%20in%20place%20%E2%80%9Cto%20protect%20these%20rights%20against%20State%20action%E2%80%9D.%20If%20there%20are%20restrictions%20and%20challenges%2C%20including%20the%20criminal%20mobs%20directed%20by%20the%20upper%20caste%20supremacist%20organisations%20or%20the%20police%20then%20one%20must%20test%20the%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20health%20at%20the%20courts.%20These%20judicial%20tests%20may%20be%20disappointing.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fromila-thapar-jnu-indian-history%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERomila%20Thapar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20others%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20with%20a%20public%20interest%20litigation%20questioning%20the%20arrests%20of%20activists%20and%20academics%20in%20the%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20case%20and%20sought%20an%20independent%20enquiry%20into%20the%20events.%20Her%20plea%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Factivists-arrests-supreme-court-rejects-review-petition-filed-by-romila-thapar-and-others%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edismissed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20only%20through%20the%20ratios%20discovered%20between%20the%20free%20associations%20and%20the%20assemblies%20for%20an%20egalitarian%20world%2C%20and%20the%20opposition%20to%20these%20actions%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emafia%20famiglia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20state%20institutions%20that%20we%20can%20diagnose%20the%20health%20of%20the%20Indian%20Union.%20In%20the%20same%20way%2C%20the%20ratio%20of%20the%20outcomes%20of%20the%20petitions%20placed%20before%20the%20judiciary%20and%20the%20guarantees%20of%20the%20constitution%20alone%20can%20tell%20us%20of%20the%20salubriousness%20or%20otherwise%20of%20the%20institutions%20of%20the%20constitution.%20Or%20help%20us%20gauge%20the%20length%20of%20time%20that%20the%20present%20fascistic%20political%20situation%20has%20borrowed%20from%20the%20deferred%20revolution%20of%20the%20lower%20caste%20majority%20for%20an%20egalitarian%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShaj%20Mohan%20and%20Divya%20Dwivedi%20are%20philosophers%20based%20in%20the%20Subcontinent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693392314000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F23122754%2FScreenshot-2023-06-23-at-12.27.26-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-constitutional