0fight%20and%20the%20coronavirus%20vaccine.%20It%20is%20set%20to%20release%20on%2028%20September%202023%2C%20coinciding%20with%20the%20release%20of%20'Salaar'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvivek-agnihotris-meme-trolling-shah-rukh-khans-jawan-and-prabhas-salaar-goes-viral%2Farticleshow%2F103210600.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kremlin%20says%20Prigozhin%20plane%20crash%20may%20have%20been%20caused%20deliberately%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693391451000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103211155%2Cimgsize-74476.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fkremlin-says-prigozhin-plane-crash-may-have-been-caused-deliberately%2Farticleshow%2F103210615.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103210615.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Kremlin%20has%20acknowledged%20the%20possibility%20that%20the%20plane%20crash%20that%20killed%20mercenary%20boss%20Yevgeny%20Prigozhin%20may%20have%20been%20deliberate.%20The%20cause%20of%20the%20crash%2C%20which%20occurred%20on%20August%2023%20and%20killed%20all%2010%20people%20on%20board%2C%20including%20two%20other%20top%20Wagner%20figures%2C%20is%20still%20unclear.%20Russia%20has%20informed%20Brazil%20that%20it%20will%20not%20probe%20the%20crash%20under%20international%20rules.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fkremlin-says-prigozhin-plane-crash-may-have-been-caused-deliberately%2Farticleshow%2F103210615.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fkremlin-says-prigozhin-plane-crash-may-have-been-caused-deliberately%2Famp_articleshow%2F103210615.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fkremlin-says-prigozhin-plane-crash-may-have-been-caused-deliberately%2Famp_articleshow%2F103210615.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Police%20in%20Maharashtra%20Are%20Obstructing%20Events%20To%20Discuss%20a%20Book%20on%20Ishrat%20Jahan%20Encounter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30143009%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-30-at-2.12.42-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Since%20January%20this%20year%2C%20human%20rights%20activist%20and%20ex-prisoner%20Wahid%20Shaikh%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20promote%20his%20recently%20published%20book%20%3Cem%3EIshrat%20Jahan%20Encounter%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20book%20he%20says%20brings%20out%20the%20truth%20behind%20the%20alleged%20fake%20encounter%20killing%20of%20the%2019-year-old%20college%20student.%20The%20book%20release%20event%2C%20however%2C%20has%20been%20stalled%20each%20time%20and%20the%20police%20%E2%80%93%20while%20denying%20permission%20%E2%80%93%20have%20claimed%20that%20since%20the%20book%20is%20%E2%80%9Canti-government%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20cannot%20allow%20a%20public%20event%20or%20discussion%20around%20the%20book.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%2026%2C%20at%20an%20event%20organised%20in%20Bhiwandi%2C%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20police%20revoked%20permission%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20event%20would%20attract%20the%20wrath%20of%20Hindu%20organisations%20in%20the%20vicinity.%20Navid%20Ahmed%20Momin%2C%20the%20organiser%20and%20a%20local%20rights%20activist%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20first%20approached%20the%20police%20on%20August%2012%20for%20the%20requisite%20permission.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20handed%20over%20a%20letter%2C%20the%20names%20of%20the%20speakers%20and%20also%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20book.%20But%20for%20an%20entire%20week%2C%20the%20police%20kept%20asking%20me%20to%20keep%20visiting%20the%20police%20station.%20They%20refused%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20letter%2C%E2%80%9D%20Momin%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20just%20days%20before%20the%20event%2C%20the%20senior%20police%20inspector%20(PI)%20of%20Nizampur%20police%20station%20issued%20a%20letter%2C%20rejecting%20permission%20for%20the%20meeting.%20In%20the%20letter%2C%20senior%20PI%20Naresh%20Pawar%20claims%20that%20since%20the%20book%20is%20%E2%80%9Canti-government%E2%80%9D%20and%20has%20garnered%20%E2%80%9Cenough%20controversy%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20past%2C%20it%20could%20trigger%20objection%20from%20the%20Hindu%20right-wing%20groups%20in%20the%20vicinity.%20For%20these%20reasons%2C%20he%20cannot%20allow%20the%20event%20to%20take%20place%2C%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20book%2C%20published%20eight%20months%20ago%20in%20Urdu%2C%20had%20a%20limited%20reach%20and%20has%20not%20particularly%20led%20to%20any%20public%20discourse%20so%20far.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20tried%20contacting%20Pawar%20several%20times%20%E2%80%93%20both%20on%20his%20personal%20phone%20number%20and%20at%20the%20police%20station%20%E2%80%93%20but%20is%20yet%20to%20get%20any%20response.%20The%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20Pawar%20responds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShaikh%20was%20arrested%20in%202006%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20July%2011%2C%202006%20Mumbai%20serial%20train%20blasts%20case.%20He%20suffered%20a%20prolonged%20incarceration%20for%20about%20nine%20years%2C%20after%20which%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fabdul-wahid-shaikh-acquitted-interview%5C%22%3Eacquitted%20of%20all%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20special%20MCOCA%20court.%20Shaikh%2C%20while%20in%20jail%2C%20began%20writing%20his%20memoir%2C%20which%20was%20later%20published%20in%20Urdu%20and%20subsequently%20translated%20into%20multiple%20languages.%20Shaikh%20has%20also%20continued%20to%20advocate%20for%20the%20others%20implicated%20in%20the%20case%20and%20convicted.%20Shaikh%20maintains%20that%2C%20like%20him%2C%20the%20others%20convicted%20in%20the%20case%20are%20all%20innocent%20and%20were%20made%20scapegoats%20by%20the%20Mumbai%20police.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShaikh%E2%80%99s%20book%20on%20the%20Ishrat%20Jahan%20encounter%20killing%20is%20based%20on%20information%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20the%20CBI%20investigation%20into%20the%20case%20and%20interviews%20of%20her%20mother%20and%20other%20family%20members.%20Jahan%2C%20a%20teenage%20woman%20from%20Mumbra%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20June%202004%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20police%20in%20an%20%E2%80%98encounter%E2%80%99%20along%20with%20three%20men.%20A%20magisterial%20enquiry%2C%20an%20SIT%20probe%20and%20a%20CBI%20investigation%20subsequently%20all%20concluded%20that%20this%20was%20a%20fake%20encounter%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20police%20claim%20of%20having%20fired%20on%20her%20in%20%E2%80%98self-defence%E2%80%99%20was%20a%20lie.%20In%20July%202013%2C%20almost%20a%20decade%20after%20the%20fake%20encounter%2C%20a%20chargesheet%20was%20filed%20against%20seven%20Gujarat%20police%20officials%20and%20(in%20a%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20in%20February%202014)%20four%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20officials%20for%20the%20unlawful%20killings%2C%20abduction%2C%20criminal%20conspiracy%20etc.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CBI%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-many-deaths-of-ishrat-jahan%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einvestigation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20pointed%20to%20evidence%20of%20the%20possibility%20that%20the%20fake%20encounter%20had%20the%20prior%20approval%20of%20the%20then%20Gujarat%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20even%20the%20chief%20minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2Fishrat_jahan7591.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22838%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2Fishrat_jahan7591.jpg%20759w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2Fishrat_jahan7591-300x167.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-23425%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22466%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20file%20photo%20of%20Ishrat%20Jahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20organising%20a%20public%20event%20in%20Bhiwandi%2C%20Shaikh%20had%20tried%20to%20organise%20similar%20book%20discussions%20in%20Mumbra%2C%20Jalgaon%20and%20Pune%20%E2%80%93%20all%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Each%20time%2C%20the%20police%2C%20he%20says%2C%20tried%20to%20stop%20the%20event%2C%20claiming%20that%20it%20was%20controversial%20and%20against%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20government.%20While%20the%20Jalgaon%20and%20Pune%20events%20were%20cancelled%2C%20the%20ones%20in%20Bhiwandi%20and%20Mumbra%20continued%20amidst%20police%20pushback%20and%20alleged%20threats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Bhiwandi%2C%20the%20police%20gathered%20in%20large%20numbers%2C%20Momin%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20small%20event%20and%20open%20only%20to%20the%20invitees.%20We%20had%20told%20the%20police%20that%20not%20more%20than%2040-50%20people%20would%20be%20attending%20the%20event.%20Still%2C%20the%20police%20didn%E2%80%99t%20grant%20us%20permission.%20Instead%2C%20they%20converged%20in%20large%20numbers%20at%20the%20event%2C%20filming%20and%20documenting%20every%20attendee.%20They%20wanted%20to%20intimidate%20those%20attending%20the%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20Momin%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%2C%20Momin%20claims%2C%20have%20not%20read%20the%20book%20as%20it%20is%20only%20published%20in%20Urdu%20so%20far.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20the%20author%20has%20actually%20written%20in%20the%20book.%20But%20they%20are%20so%20scared%20of%20disappointing%20their%20masters%20%5Bthe%20BJP%20government%5D%20that%20they%20are%20going%20all%20out%20to%20stop%20a%20book%20from%20reaching%20the%20public.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693391446000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F30143009%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-08-30-at-2.12.42-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpolice-maharashtra-obstruct-events-ishrat-jahan-book-wahid-shaikh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20book%20written%20by%20Wahidh%20Shaikh%2C%20who%20was%20falsely%20implicated%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20serial%20train%20blasts%20case%2C%20is%20based%20on%20public%20information%2C%20the%20CBI's%20investigation%20and%20interviews%20of%20family%20members.%20But%20the%20police%20claim%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Banti-government%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpolice-maharashtra-obstruct-events-ishrat-jahan-book-wahid-shaikh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chitrangda%20Singh's%20most%20glam%20avatars!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693391400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103204861%2Cimgsize-54124.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fchitrangda-singhs-most-glam-avatars%2Fphotostory%2F103204861.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A