t%20Judge%20Abual%20Hasnat%20Muhammad%20Zulqarnain%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThat%20accused%20Imran%20Khan%20Niazi%20s%2Fo%20Ikramullah%20Khan%20Niazi%20r%2Fo%20Zaman%20Park%2C%20Lahore%20is%20hereby%20ordered%20for%20judicial%20remand%20in%20case%20FIR%20mentioned%20above%2C%20who%20is%20already%20detained%20in%20district%20jail%2C%20Attock.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20a%20notification%20issued%20by%20the%20law%20ministry%20said%20the%20interior%20ministry%20had%20conveyed%20security%20concerns%20to%20it%20in%20a%20letter%20today%20the%20Law%20and%20Justice%20Division%20had%20%E2%80%9Cno%20objection%E2%80%9D%20to%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20trial%20in%20the%20cipher%20case%20being%20held%20at%20Attock%20jail%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20lawyers%2C%20Gohar%20Khan%2C%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EAFP%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0by%20phone%20that%20the%20ex-premier%20was%20%E2%80%9Carrested%20%5Bin%20the%20cipher%20case%5D%20prior%20to%20today%E2%80%99s%20court%20ruling.%20The%20exact%20date%20of%20his%20arrest%20remains%20unclear%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%2C%20Muhammad%20Shoaib%20Shaheen%2C%20said%20%E2%80%9Chis%20legal%20team%20was%20intentionally%20left%20uninformed%20and%20kept%20in%20the%20dark.%20This%20constitutes%20a%20manipulation%20of%20justice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cipher%20case%20pertains%20to%20a%20diplomatic%20document%20which%20reportedly%20went%20missing%20from%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20possession.%20The%20PTI%20alleges%20that%20it%20contained%20a%20threat%20from%20the%20United%20States%20to%20oust%20Imran%20from%20power.%20Proceedings%20against%20PTI%20Vice%20Chairman%20and%20former%20foreign%20minister%20Shah%20Mahmood%20Qureshi%20in%20the%20same%20case%20are%20also%20under%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20much-anticipated%20order%20in%20the%20Toshakhana%20case%20was%20announced%20by%20an%20IHC%20division%20bench%20comprising%20Chief%20Justice%20Aamer%20Farooq%20and%20Justice%20Tariq%20Mehmood%20Jahan%C2%ADgiri%20on%20the%20former%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20against%20his%20prison%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20copy%20of%20the%20judgment%20will%20be%20available%20shortly%20%E2%80%A6%20all%20we%20are%20saying%20now%20is%20that%20%5BImran%E2%80%99s%5D%20request%20has%20been%20approved%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Farooq%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20order%20issued%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20the%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20three-year%20jail%20term%20awarded%20to%20Imran%20%E2%80%9Cqualifies%20as%20a%20short%20sentence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20arguments%20raised%20by%20both%20sides%20as%20to%20the%20jurisdiction%20and%20other%20issues%20involve%20a%20deeper%20appreciation%20of%20the%20matter%20which%20at%20the%20stage%20is%20not%20warranted%2C%20especially%2C%20where%20the%20sentence%20is%20a%20short%20one%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20pointed%20out%20in%20the%20order%20that%20even%20though%20long%20arguments%20were%20presented%20by%20both%20sides%2C%20such%20questions%20were%20left%20to%20be%20decided%20at%20the%20stage%20when%20the%20appeal%20was%20taken%20up%20for%20adjudication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20above%20reasons%2C%20the%20instant%20application%20is%20allowed%20and%20the%20sentence%20awarded%20by%20the%20trial%20court%20dated%20Aug%205%20is%20suspended%3B%20consequently%2C%20the%20applicant%20is%20ordered%20to%20be%20released%20on%20bail%20in%20the%20instant%20matter%20subject%20to%20furnishing%20bail%20bonds%20in%20the%20sum%20of%20Rs100%2C000%20with%20one%20surety%20in%20the%20like%20amount%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20the%20deputy%20registrar%20(judicial)%20of%20this%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20ruled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%205%2C%20a%20trial%20court%20in%20Islamabad%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1768528%2Fimran-arrested-after-islamabad-court-finds-him-guilty-of-corrupt-practices-in-toshakhana-case%5C%22%3Econvicted%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20PTI%20chief%20in%20the%20case%20filed%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20(ECP)%20that%20involved%20concealing%20details%20of%20state%20gifts%20and%20jailed%20him%20for%20three%20years.%20The%20verdict%20meant%20he%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1769083%5C%22%3Edisqualified%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%20contesting%20general%20elections%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImran%20had%20subsequently%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1769060%5C%22%3Efiled%20an%20appeal%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20high%20court%20against%20his%20conviction.%20He%20had%20also%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20(SC)%20against%20the%20IHC%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1768450%5C%22%3Eremand%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20case%20back%20to%20the%20trial%20court%20judge%20who%20had%20convicted%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20however%2C%20the%20SC%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1771864%5C%22%3Eacknowledged%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cprocedural%20defects%E2%80%9D%20in%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20conviction%20but%20had%20opted%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20IHC%20decision%20on%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20plea.%20The%20court%E2%80%99s%20observations%20had%20drawn%20the%20ire%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Bar%20Council%2C%20which%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1771901%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0there%20should%20be%20no%20%E2%80%9Cinterference%E2%80%9D%20in%20matters%20pending%20before%20the%20subordinate%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20ago%2C%20ECP%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20Advocate%20Amjad%20Pervaiz%20concluded%20his%20arguments%20and%20urged%20the%20court%20to%20issue%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20state%20to%20make%20it%20a%20respondent%20in%20the%20case.%20For%20his%20part%2C%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20lawyer%20Latif%20Khosa%20had%20said%20he%20had%20no%20objections%20to%20Pervaiz%E2%80%99s%20plea%20but%20had%20also%20expressed%20that%20the%20action%20was%20not%20required%20by%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20proceedings%2C%20a%20large%20contingent%20of%20Islamabad%20police%20stood%20guard%E2%80%99s%20outside%20the%20IHC.%20The%20PTI%20legal%20team%20and%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20sisters%20Aleema%20Khan%20and%20Uzma%20Khan%20were%20among%20those%20who%20attended%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1772860%2Fimrans-toshakhana-sentence-suspended-but-detention-at-attock-jail-to-continue-in-cipher-case%23pti-demands-imrans-release-today%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Permalink%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3EPTI%20demands%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20release%20today%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20development%2C%20the%20PTI%20demanded%20that%20Imran%20should%20be%20released%20from%20jail%20today.%20A%20video%20posted%20by%20the%20party%20on%20X%20showed%20lawyers%20chanting%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eriha%20karo%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Brelease%20him%5D%E2%80%9D%20outside%20the%20IHC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EGeo%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20PTI%20Barrister%20Ali%20Zafar%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20high%20court%20has%20fulfilled%20the%20requirements%20of%20justice.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20tell%20you%20why%3A%20Aside%20from%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20Toshakhana%20case%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20baseless%20%E2%80%94%20the%20trial%20judge%20did%20not%20allow%20Imran%20to%20submit%20witnesses%20in%20his%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20witnesses%20in%20one%E2%80%99s%20defence%20are%20not%20allowed%2C%20there%20is%20no%20greater%20%5Bexample%20of%20a%5D%20mistrial.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20clarified%20that%20for%20now%20only%20the%20sentence%20has%20been%20suspended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20lawyer%20Shoaib%20Shaheen%2C%20while%20talking%20to%20media%20outside%20the%20IHC%2C%20said%20Imran%20should%20be%20provided%20compensation%20for%20the%20number%20of%20days%20he%20was%20kept%20behind%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20PTI%20Information%20Secretary%20Raoof%20Hasan%2C%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20in%20any%20other%20case%20after%20the%20suspension%20of%20his%20sentence%20in%20the%20Toshakhana%20case%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cill-intentioned%20and%20mala%20fide%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20fortunate%20to%20be%20witnessing%20the%20re-scripting%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20political%20and%20legal%20history%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Cjustice%20shall%20prevail%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20National%20Assembly%20speaker%20Asad%20Qaiser%20said%20the%20suspension%20of%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20sentence%20confirmed%20that%20the%20Toshakhana%20verdict%20was%20announced%20%E2%80%9Cin%20haste%E2%80%9D%20and%20did%20not%20give%20the%20PTI%20chief%20a%20chance%20to%20defend%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20stated%20that%20if%20Imran%20was%20arrested%20in%20another%20case%2C%20it%20would%20be%20an%20attempt%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpush%20the%20country%20towards%20anarchy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20leader%20Taimur%20Khan%20Jhagra%20said%20the%20nation%20expected%20Imran%20to%20be%20released%20from%20jail%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%E2%80%98abuse%20of%20the%20law%E2%80%99%20campaign%20against%20Imran%20Khan%20has%20sunk%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20systems%20far%20enough.%20We%20cannot%20afford%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenator%20Faisal%20Javed%20Khan%20posted%20verses%20from%20the%20Holy%20Quran%20expressing%20gratitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20PML-N%20expressed%20its%20displeasure%20towards%20today%E2%80%99s%20outcome%2C%20with%20party%20president%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20saying%20that%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20sentence%20had%20been%20suspended%20and%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20terminated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20message%20of%20%E2%80%99%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1752496%5C%22%3Egood%20to%20see%20you%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20%E2%80%98wish%20you%20good%20luck%E2%80%99%20has%20reached%20the%20IHC%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20claiming%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceveryone%20knew%20about%20the%20verdict%20before%20it%20was%20even%20announced%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20moment%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20for%20our%20justice%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shehbaz%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20clear%20message%20is%20received%20from%20the%20higher%20judiciary%2C%20what%20else%20should%20the%20subordinate%20court%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20law%20minister%20Azam%20Nazeer%20Tarar%20said%20that%20the%20detailed%20verdict%20had%20not%20been%20released.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20IHC%20had%20only%20suspended%20the%20sentence%20as%20that%20was%20the%20matter%20pending%20before%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20a%20short%20sentence.%20Ordinarily%2C%20sentences%20are%20suspended%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asserted%20that%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20disqualification%20had%20not%20ended.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20only%20suspension%20of%20sentence%20which%20means%20that%20he%20be%20set%20free%20in%20this%20case%20if%20he%20is%20not%20wanted%20or%20arrested%20in%20another.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20there%20is%20no%20other%20definition%20or%20meaning%20of%20suspension%20of%20sentence.%20Neither%20his%20punishment%20nor%20his%20qualification%20have%20been%20ended%20or%20even%20the%20declaration%20that%20he%20was%20dishonest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Tarar%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20comment%20further%20as%20the%20detailed%20verdict%20had%20not%20been%20released.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20suspension%20of%20the%20sentence%20could%20be%20challenged%2C%20again%20reiterating%20that%20the%20detailed%20reasons%20had%20not%20been%20issued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20last%20night%2C%20former%20interior%20minister%20Rana%20Sanaullah%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHe%20%5BImran%5D%20will%20not%20come%20outside%20%5Bof%20the%20jail%5D%20%E2%80%94%20release%20is%20not%20possible%2C%20%5Bhe%5D%20will%20have%20to%20face%20the%20prosecution%20in%20other%20cases!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1772860%2Fimrans-toshakhana-sentence-suspended-but-detention-at-attock-jail-to-continue-in-cipher-case%23suspension-of-sentence-does-not-affect-status-of-conviction%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Permalink%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Suspension%20of%20sentence%20does%20not%20affect%20status%20of%20conviction%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EDawnNewsTV%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Barrister%20Asad%20Rahim%20Khan%20said%20that%20typically%20the%20suspension%20of%20a%20sentence%20did%20not%20affect%20the%20status%20of%20the%20conviction.%20%E2%80%9CConviction%20means%20you%20have%20been%20held%20responsible%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20law.%20So%20only%20when%20you%20are%20completely%20acquitted%20in%20an%20appeal%20does%20it%E2%80%9D%20end%20the%20disqualification%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahim%20said%20that%20the%20detailed%20verdict%20was%20awaited%20to%20see%20whether%20the%20court%20had%20said%20anything%20about%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20disqualification.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20keep%20this%20only%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20the%20sentence%2C%20then%20it%20has%20no%20relation%20to%20disqualification%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20PTI%20lawyers%20filing%20another%20plea%20seeking%20a%20bar%20on%20arresting%20Imran%20in%20any%20other%20case%2C%20Rahim%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20bar%20on%20requesting%20the%20courts%20to%20restrain%20law%20enforcement%20bodies%20from%20unlawfully%20arresting%20an%20accused%3B%20but%20the%20ex-premier%20would%20nonetheless%20have%20to%20face%20the%20cases%20registered%20against%20him%20on%20an%20individual%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20after%20a%20sentence%20was%20suspended%2C%20there%20were%20some%20procedural%20formalities%20which%20needed%20to%20be%20completed.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20hoped%20and%20written%20in%20a%20sentence%20that%20if%20the%20person%20is%20not%20required%20in%20another%20case%2C%20he%20should%20be%20set%20at%20liberty%2C%20meaning%20he%20should%20be%20set%20free%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20said%20that%20the%20same%20should%20be%20done%20in%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20case%20but%20noted%20that%20there%20were%20many%20cases%20registered%20against%20the%20PTI%20chief.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20suspension%20of%20the%20sentence%20could%20be%20challenged%20in%20the%20apex%20court.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20challenge%20this%20order%2C%20the%20state%20can%20come%20into%20action.%20But%20the%20next%20question%20will%20be%20how%20the%20SC%20considers%20its%20own%20precedents%20in%20reply%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1772860%2Fimrans-toshakhana-sentence-suspended-but-detention-at-attock-jail-to-continue-in-cipher-case%23pti-seeks-bar-on-imrans-arrest-in-other-cases%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Permalink%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3EPTI%20seeks%20bar%20on%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20in%20other%20cases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20legal%20team%20filed%20a%20fresh%20petition%20in%20the%20IHC%20today%20seeking%20directives%20to%20refrain%20authorities%20from%20further%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20and%20unjustified%20arrest%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20former%20premier%20in%20any%20case%20filed%20against%20him%20after%20August%205%2C%20when%20he%20was%20convicted%20in%20the%20Toshakhana%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20available%20with%C2%A0%3Cem%3EDawn.com%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20mentions%20the%20cipher%20case%20as%20one%20of%20the%20FIRs%20under%20which%20the%20PTI%20chief%20is%20seeking%20protection%20from%20arrest.%20The%20FIA%20had%20last%20week%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1772385%5C%22%3Egrilled%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Imran%20in%20the%20said%20case%2C%20which%20invokes%20the%20Official%20Secrets%20Act%2C%20for%20over%20an%20hour%20at%20the%20Attock%20Jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFiled%20through%20Barrister%20Salman%20Safdar%2C%20the%20petition%20named%20the%20state%20as%20a%20respondent%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20cipher%20case%20had%20been%20filed%20against%20Imran%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20malafide%20intentions%E2%80%9D%20and%20termed%20it%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbogus%20nature%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plea%20stated%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Conly%20remedy%20available%20to%20avoid%20unjustified%2C%20illegal%20and%20straightaway%20arrest%E2%80%9D%20was%20by%20invoking%20Article%2010%20(safeguards%20as%20to%20arrest%20and%20detention)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprotection%20of%20his%20fundamental%20rights%20and%20safeguards%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20further%20said%20that%20the%20petitioner%20would%20%E2%80%9Csuffer%20irreparable%20loss%20in%20case%20he%20is%20arrested%20for%20another%20offence%2C%20which%20he%20has%20not%20committed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20expressed%20the%20apprehension%20that%20the%20PTI%20chief%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20adversaries%20and%20opponents%20would%20be%20able%20to%20further%20their%20nefarious%20designs%20and%20political%20ambitions%20in%20the%20absence%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20IHC%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ckind%20intervention%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1772860%2Fimrans-toshakhana-sentence-suspended-but-detention-at-attock-jail-to-continue-in-cipher-case%23toshakhana-case%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Permalink%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3EToshakhana%20case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%2C%20filed%20by%20lawmakers%20of%20the%20then%20coalition%20government%2C%20was%20based%20on%20a%20criminal%20complaint%20filed%20by%20the%20ECP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20alleged%20that%20Imran%20had%20%E2%80%9Cdeliberately%20concealed%E2%80%9D%20details%20of%20the%20gifts%20he%20retained%20from%20the%20Toshaskhana%20%E2%80%94%20a%20repository%20where%20presents%20handed%20to%20government%20officials%20from%20foreign%20officials%20are%20kept%20%E2%80%94%20during%20his%20time%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20proceeds%20from%20their%20reported%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Toshakhana%20rules%2C%20gifts%2Fpresents%20and%20other%20such%20materials%20received%20by%20persons%20to%20whom%20these%20rules%20apply%20shall%20be%20reported%20to%20the%20Cabinet%20Division.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImran%20has%20faced%20a%20number%20of%20legal%20issues%20over%20his%20retention%20of%20gifts.%20The%20issue%20also%20led%20to%20his%20disqualification%20by%20the%20ECP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Oct%2021%2C%202022%2C%20the%20ECP%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1716149%5C%22%3Econcluded%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20former%20premier%20had%20indeed%20made%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%20statements%20and%20incorrect%20declarations%E2%80%9D%20regarding%20the%20gifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20watchdog%E2%80%99s%20order%20had%20said%20Imran%20stood%20disqualified%20under%20Article%2063(1)(p)%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20ECP%20had%20approached%20the%20Islamabad%20sessions%20court%20with%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20complaint%2C%20seeking%20proceedings%20against%20Imran%20under%20criminal%20law%20for%20allegedly%20misleading%20officials%20about%20the%20gifts%20he%20received%20from%20foreign%20dignitaries%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2010%2C%20Imran%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1751998%23%3A~%3Atext%3DImran-%2Cindicted%2C-in%2520Toshakhana%2520case%5C%22%3Eindicted%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20case.%20However%2C%20on%20July%204%2C%20the%20IHC%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1762926%5C%22%3Estayed%20the%20proceeding%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20directed%20ADSJ%20Dilawar%20to%20re-examine%20the%20matter%20in%20seven%20days%2C%20keeping%20in%20view%20eight%20legal%20questions%20he%20framed%20to%20decide%20the%20maintainability%20of%20the%20Toshakhana%20reference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20questions%20had%20included%20whether%20the%20complaint%20was%20filed%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20ECP%20by%20a%20duly%20authorised%20person%2C%20whether%20the%20ECP%E2%80%99s%20decision%20of%20Oct%2021%2C%202022%2C%20was%20a%20valid%20authorisation%20to%20any%20officer%20of%20ECP%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%2C%20and%20whether%20the%20question%20of%20authorisation%20was%20a%20question%20of%20fact%20and%20evidence%20and%20could%20be%20ratified%20subsequently%20during%20the%20course%20of%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20on%20July%209%2C%20ADSJ%20Dilawar%20while%20ruling%20that%20the%20reference%20was%20maintainable%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1763747%5C%22%3Erevi%C2%ADved%20the%20stalled%20proceedings%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20summoned%20the%20witne%C2%ADsses%20for%20testimony.%20The%20decision%20was%20subsequently%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1764274%5C%22%3Echallenged%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20IHC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%202%2C%20Judge%20Dilawar%20had%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1768275%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDilawar%252C%2520on%2520Wednesday%252C-%2Cruled%2C-that%2520Mr%2520Khan%25E2%2580%2599s%5C%22%3Eruled%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20Imran%E2%80%99s%20legal%20team%20failed%20to%20prove%20the%20relevance%20of%20his%20witnesses.%20He%20had%20warned%20the%20defence%20counsel%20to%20conclude%20the%20arguments%2C%20or%20else%20the%20court%20would%20reserve%20an%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IHC%20then%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1768450%2Fsome-respite-for-imran-as-toshakhana-c