0he%20was%20insulted%2C%20his%20darbaris%20(courtiers)%20felt%20so%20and%20brought%20this%20proposal%20against%20me.%20I%20came%20to%20know%20that%20(the%20matter)%20has%20been%20referred%20to%20the%20privileges%20committee%20and%20I%20have%20been%20suspended%20till%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20MP%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20then%20hit%20out%20at%20its%20leader's%20suspension%2C%20calling%20the%20move%20%26quot%3Bundemocratic%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693384680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F371e2mtg_adhir-ranjan-chowdhary_625x300_19_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadhir-ranjan-chowdhury-lok-sabha-privileges-committee-key-lok-sabha-panel-asks-speaker-to-revoke-congress-leaders-suspension-4341893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Privileges%20Committee%20of%20Parliament%20has%20adopted%20a%20resolution%20to%20revoke%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury's%20suspension%20from%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20recommended%20this%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadhir-ranjan-chowdhury-lok-sabha-privileges-committee-key-lok-sabha-panel-asks-speaker-to-revoke-congress-leaders-suspension-4341893%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadhir-ranjan-chowdhury-lok-sabha-privileges-committee-key-lok-sabha-panel-asks-speaker-to-revoke-congress-leaders-suspension-4341893%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadhir-ranjan-chowdhury-lok-sabha-privileges-committee-key-lok-sabha-panel-asks-speaker-to-revoke-congress-leaders-suspension-4341893%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3BK%3A%20Why%20a%20Top%20IAS%20Officer%20Has%20Sought%20a%20CBI%20Probe%20Into%20the%20Flagship%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F02213735%2FTap-water.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Punching%20holes%20in%20the%20narrative%20of%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20governance%E2%80%9D%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20a%20top%20IAS%20officer%20has%20sought%20a%20probe%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20into%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20a%20Rs%2013%2C000%20crore%20centrally-sponsored%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%2C%20the%201992-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20Ashok%20Kumar%20Parmar%2C%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-ias-dalit-lg-manoj-sinha-harassment-humiliation%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20J%26amp%3BK%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20(LG)%20Manoj%20Sinha%20of%20being%20part%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccriminal%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20incumbent%20chief%20secretary%20Arun%20Kumar%20Mehta%20to%20commit%20irregularities%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20flagship%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20(JJM)%20scheme%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%2C%20which%20was%20rolled%20out%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%202019%2C%20aims%20to%20provide%20piped%20drinking%20water%20to%20all%20the%20rural%20households%20in%20the%20country%20by%202024.%20Under%20the%20scheme%2C%20a%20central%20grant%20of%20Rs%2013%2C259%20crore%20was%20approved%20for%20J%26amp%3BK%20%E2%80%93%20of%20which%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore%20is%20meant%20only%20for%20procuring%20pipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%2C%20who%20is%20presently%20serving%20as%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Public%20Standards%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20has%20alleged%20in%20a%20complaint%20to%20the%20Union%20home%20secretary%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Bhalla%20that%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20overlooked%20official%20guidelines%20and%20financial%20rules%2C%20and%20tainted%20officers%20were%20%E2%80%9Carbitrarily%E2%80%9D%20posted%20at%20key%20positions%20to%20commit%20irregularities%20in%20the%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20claims%20that%20a%20conspiracy%20was%20hatched%20by%20the%20chief%20secretary%20to%20procure%20pipes%20worth%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20norms%20of%20the%20JJM%20scheme.%20He%20said%20that%20pipes%20worth%20Rs%2028%20crore%2C%20which%20are%20%E2%80%9Cunsuitable%20for%20hilly%20areas%E2%80%9D%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20were%20already%20purchased%20by%20the%20administration%20%E2%80%93%20allegedly%20without%20administrative%20approval%20and%20technical%20sanction%20and%20in%20violation%20of%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20has%20also%20alleged%20in%20another%20complaint%20on%20July%2018%2C%20accessed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20a%20purchase%20committee%20headed%20by%20the%20chief%20engineer%20(Kashmir)%20of%20the%20Jal%20Shakti%20department%20floated%20tenders%20for%20ductile%20iron%20pipes%20worth%20Rs%20690%20crore%20without%20getting%20administrative%20approval%20per%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tender%20was%20floated%20in%20January%202022%20and%20the%20orders%20were%20placed%20in%20June%202022%20under%20non-JJM%20specification%20as%20%E2%80%9Cpart%20of%20a%20criminal%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20by%20senior%20officials%20of%20the%20administration%2C%20the%20complaint%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20official%20reaction%20to%20the%20allegations.%20Yitesh%20Yadav%2C%20the%20media%20advisor%20to%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%2C%20and%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20secretary%20Arun%20Kumar%20Mehta%20didn%E2%80%99t%20respond%20to%20queries%20from%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20by%20the%20senior%20officer%2C%20who%20has%20served%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20for%20more%20than%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20administration%20appears%20to%20have%20begun%20backdoor%20efforts%20to%20question%20Parmar%E2%80%99s%20record.%20A%20news%20report%20citing%20unnamed%20%E2%80%9Csources%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Frisingkashmir.com%2Fias-officer-ashok-parmars-career-marked-by-disputes-inefficiency-sources-816b7332-3076-47f2-a4bb-fa64a5db74db%5C%22%3ERising%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20says%20the%20IAS%20officer%E2%80%99s%20career%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cmarked%20by%20disputes%2C%20inefficiency%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F01180244%2FEfZRdMaU0AAfEzt.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22942%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F01180244%2FEfZRdMaU0AAfEzt.jpeg%20942w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F01180244%2FEfZRdMaU0AAfEzt-300x140.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-476586%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20LG%20Manoj%20Sinha%20signed%20the%20termination%20orders.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40diprjk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20top%20J%26amp%3BK%20officer%2C%20however%2C%20rejected%20the%20allegations%2C%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthese%20people%20can%E2%80%99t%20digest%20the%20changes%E2%80%9D%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%20earlier%20system%2C%20nearly%20100%25%20allotments%20were%20done%20arbitrarily%20without%20tendering%2C%20technical%20sanction%2C%20etc.%20We%20are%20today%20perhaps%20No%201%20in%20digital%20governance%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20officer%20claimed%2C%20wishing%20to%20remain%20anonymous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJJM%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%3A%20a%20background%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202020%2C%20the%20Union%20Jal%20Shakti%20Ministry%20said%20that%20under%20the%20JJM%20scheme%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20was%20%E2%80%9Cplanning%20to%20achieve%20100%25%20coverage%20of%20tap%20water%20connection%E2%80%9D%20to%2018.35%20lakh%20rural%20households%20by%20December%202022%2C%20two%20years%20ahead%20of%20the%20national%20deadline.%20%E2%80%9CJ%26amp%3BK%20will%20be%20a%20leading%20example%20to%20accomplish%20the%20ambitious%20target%20of%20providing%20tap%20connection%20to%20every%20rural%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%20states%20in%20his%20complaint%20that%20the%20target%20was%20set%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20assessing%20the%20bottlenecks%20such%20as%20hostile%20terrain%20and%20extreme%20climatic%20conditions%2C%20poor%20capacity%20and%20capability%20of%20engineering%20staff%20of%20Jal%20Shakti%20Department%20and%20poor%20capacity%2C%20capability%20and%20financial%20conditions%20of%20contractors%20of%20UT%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%2C%20which%20is%20run%20directly%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%2C%20missed%20the%20December%202022%20deadline%20it%20had%20set.%20An%20official%20handout%20issued%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Directorate%20of%20Information%20and%20Public%20Relations%2C%20the%20official%20media%20wing%20of%20the%20administration%2C%20said%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20secretary%20extended%20the%20deadline%20to%20June%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20also%20been%20marked%20to%20P.K.%20Mishra%2C%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Rajiv%20Gauba%2C%20cabinet%20secretary%20%E2%80%93%20notes%20that%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20had%20planned%203%2C095%20water%20supply%20schemes%20under%20the%20JJM%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20scheme%20gone%20awry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20handout%20states%20that%20out%20of%206%2C774%20projects%20taken%20up%20under%20the%20JJM%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20only%20284%20were%20completed%20till%20February%20this%20year.%20%E2%80%9COnly%20Rs%20800%20crore%20has%20been%20utilised%20this%20year%20till%20August%202023%2C%20including%20Rs%20700%20crores%20for%20the%20procurement%20of%20pipes%20only%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmar%E2%80%99s%20letter%20to%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%2C%20dated%20August%2015%2C%202023%2C%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20data%2C%20out%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%2013%2C000%20crore%20earmarked%20for%20J%26amp%3BK%20under%20the%20JJM%20scheme%2C%20Rs%203%2C136%20crore%20has%20been%20released%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20but%20only%20Rs%202%2C336%20crore%20has%20been%20spent%20by%20J%26amp%3BK.%20The%20scheme%20has%20shown%20physical%20progress%20of%20only%2022.78%25%20till%20August%2021%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20rate%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20will%20miss%20the%20target%20set%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20by%20two%20years%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20too%20if%20Rs%204%2C000%20crore%20is%20spent%20every%20year%2C%20which%20according%20to%20Parmar%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20is%20%E2%80%9Ca%20very%20difficult%20rather%20impossible%20target%20to%20achieve%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20accused%20the%20chief%20secretary%2C%20the%20LG%E2%80%99s%20advisor%20and%20the%20chief%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Jal%20Shakti%20Department%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmisleading%E2%80%9D%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20IAS%20officer%20cites%20the%20example%20of%20Samba%20district%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20allege%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20scale%E2%80%9D%20violations%20of%20financial%20rules%20and%20vigilance%20guidelines%20in%20the%20execution%20of%20central%20schemes.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20complaint%20states%20that%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20gave%20technical%20sanction%20to%20seven%20projects%20in%20Samba%20after%20the%20contracts%20were%20already%20awarded%2C%20which%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cviolation%20of%20codal%20formalities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%20claims%20that%20these%20projects%20were%20scheduled%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20four%20months%20but%20to%20date%2C%20they%20are%20incomplete%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdigital%20and%20geo-tagged%20photographs%E2%80%9D%20and%20reports%20of%20third-party%20inspection%20and%20soil-bearing%20capacity%20from%20the%20project%20files%2C%20per%20the%20scheme%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20also%20alleges%20that%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20overlooked%20the%20violation%20of%20norms%20of%20depth%20approved%20for%20laying%20down%20underground%20water%20pipes%20and%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20projects%20such%20as%20the%20length%20of%20the%20pipes%20and%20trench%20excavation%20in%20Samba%20district%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20payment%20purpose%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20spot%20inspection%20it%20has%20been%20found%20that%20at%20many%20places%20pipes%20have%20been%20laid%20over%20ground%2C%20but%20the%20payments%20have%20been%20made%20for%20trench%20excavation%20and%20refilling%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20complaint%20alleges%2C%20adding%20that%20these%20violations%20%E2%80%9Cwere%20not%20confined%20to%20one%20district%20only%2C%20as%20similar%20irregularities%20were%20also%20reported%20by%20(J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s)%20ACB%20(Anti-Corruption%20Bureau)%20%E2%80%A6%20in%20almost%20all%20districts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20complaint%2C%20Parmar%20alleges%20that%20the%20administration%20%E2%80%9Cdid%20not%20take%20any%20action%20on%20large%20number%20of%20advisories%E2%80%9D%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20anti-corruption%20body%20and%20%E2%80%9Crewarded%E2%80%9D%20a%20young%20IAS%20officer%20from%20Kashmir%20with%20multiple%20postings%20as%20administrative%20secretary%20of%20tourism%20and%20culture%20departments%20and%20chief%20of%20Economic%20Reconstruction%20Agency%2C%20purportedly%20for%20overlooking%20violations%20of%20rules%20as%20Mission%20Director%20of%20JJM%20scheme%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20officer%20quoted%20above%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cevery%20single%20contract%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20based%20on%20e-tendering%2C%20technical%20sanction%2C%20photographic%20record%20with%20geo-coordinates%20and%20100%25%20physical%20sanction.%E2%80%9D%20He%2C%20however%2C%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20specify%20the%20number%20of%20JJM%20projects%20completed%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20referred%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20Janbhagidari%20J%26amp%3BK%20portal%2C%20an%20official%20website%20that%20shows%20the%20list%20of%20all%20the%20projects%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20without%20any%20specific%20mention%20of%20the%20JJM%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F31151926%2Fa-woman-collects-drinking-water-in-odisha_rural-sanitation_gram-vikas-1024x684.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F31151926%2Fa-woman-collects-drinking-water-in-odisha_rural-sanitation_gram-vikas-1024x684.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2F31151926%2Fa-woman-collects-drinking-water-in-odisha_rural-sanitation_gram-vikas-1024x684-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-384851%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22684%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20woman%20collects%20the%20drinking%20water%20from%20the%20third%20tap%20in%20Simlipadar%20village%20in%20Thuamul%20Rampur%2C%20Kalahandi.%20Photo%3A%20Ajaya%20Behera%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJJM%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98dismal%20status%E2%80%99%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%20alleges%20that%20as%20principal%20secretary%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Jal%20Shakti%20Department%20%E2%80%93%20the%20nodal%20body%20responsible%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20JJM%20scheme%20%E2%80%93%20he%20informed%20LG%20Sinha%2C%20chief%20secretary%20Mehta%20and%20the%20LG%E2%80%99s%20advisor%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdismal%20status%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20scheme%20which%20is%20being%20implemented%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20doing%20SWOT%20(Strengths%2C%20Weaknesses%2C%20Opportunities%2C%20and%20Threats)%20analysis%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20letter%20on%20July%2020%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20claims%20that%20Parmar%20had%20in%20a%20meeting%20on%20August%208%20last%20year%20recommended%20action%20against%20the%20chief%20engineers%20of%20Kashmir%20and%20Jammu%20divisions%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Jal%20Shakti%20Department%20for%20poor%20execution%20of%20the%20JJM%20scheme.%20While%20one%20of%20the%20officers%20was%20suspended%2C%20no%20action%20was%20taken%20against%20the%20second%20officer%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Chighly%20objectionable%20and%20arbitrary%E2%80%9D%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%2C%20who%20was%20transferred%20four%20times%20last%20year%2C%20also%20claimed%20to%20have%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20%E2%80%9Cinappropriate%20and%20premature%20transfers%20and%20postings%20of%20IAS%20officers%E2%80%9D%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20with%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry.%20In%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20Parmar%20has%20accused%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20LG%20and%20chief%20secretary%20of%20%E2%80%9Charassment%2C%20intimidation%20and%20threats%E2%80%9D%20while%20alleging%20that%20his%20frequent%20transfers%20were%20due%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbias%20and%20prejudice%E2%80%9D%20against%20him%20for%20%E2%80%9Cbeing%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20IAS%20officer%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20IAS%2FJKAS%2FIRS%20officers%20are%20given%20the%20charge%20of%20two%20to%20three%20departments%20without%20considering%20their%20seniority%20and%20experience%20and%20many%20of%20them%20are%20allowed%20to%20continue%20to%20hold%20post%2Fs%20more%20than%203%20years%20of%20prescribed%20tenure%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20complaint%20to%20the%20home%20ministry%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20by%20Parmar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Bharuch%20district%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20also%20accuses%20a%20top%20IAS%20officer%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20of%20failing%20to%20complete%20an%20inquiry%20against%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctainted%20officer%E2%80%9D%20for%20%E2%80%9Ccost%20and%20time%20overrun%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20project%20in%20Jammu%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccriminal%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20allegedly%20to%20post%20him%20in%20a%20key%20department%20responsible%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20JJM%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20despite%20the%20officer%20allegedly%20not%20being%20eligible%20for%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%20has%20also%20accused%20the%20officer%20of%20violating%20the%20order%20of%20the%20LG%2C%20which%20had%20empowered%20divisional%20and%20district%20officers%20to%20issue%20transfer%20orders%20of%20low-%20and%20middle-rung%20officials%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Revenue%20and%20Jal%20Shakti%20departments%2C%20by%20centralising%20these%20powers%20in%20his%20office%20%E2%80%9Cas%20a%20reward%20for%20committing%20all%20administrative%20and%20financial%20irregularities%20in%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20September%202022%20to%20March%202023%20in%20blatant%20violation%20of%20the%20transfer%20policy%20of%20the%20government%2C%20many%20engineers%20were%20transferred%20prematurely%20within%20two%20to%20three%20months%20with%20or%20without%20approval%20of%20LG%2C%20CS%20or%20Advisor%20Bhatnagar%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20request%20you%20to%20kindly%20urgent%20take%20necessary%20action%20by%20direct