%3E%20(a%20Karnataka%20speciality%20made%20with%20horse%20gram%20in%20spicy%20coconut%20gravy)%20and%20%3Cem%3Esevige%20kaihaalu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20sweet%20coconut%20milk%20side%20dish).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20that%20as%20he%20sees%20so%20many%20people%20now%20starting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290101%2Fbest-homestay-in-himachal-pradesh-sainj-valley-eco-friendly-kath-kuni-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomestays%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Shreedev%20says%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20first%20understand%20nature%20before%20doing%20so.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20to%20take%20in%20what%20the%20hills%20are%20telling%20you%20before%20you%20dive%20into%20this%20venture%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20this%20remarkable%20journey%20commercially%20since%202005%2C%20the%20couple%20reiterates%20that%20for%20them%20Woodway%20Estate%20has%20never%20been%20a%20structure%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20%E2%80%9Cliving%20thing%E2%80%9D%20that%20has%20grown%20with%20them%20through%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWould%20we%20have%20done%20it%20any%20other%20way%3F%E2%80%9D%20Shreedev%20thinks%20aloud%20to%20himself%20for%20a%20moment.%20%E2%80%9CDefinitely%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20a%20smile.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692605280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FWoodway-5114_11zon-1692368858-scaled.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D327701%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Susmita%20and%20Shreedev's%20Woodway%20Estate%2C%20tucked%20in%20Chikmagalur%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Western%20Ghats%2C%20is%20a%20paradise%20for%20any%20nature%20lover.%20The%20freshly%20brewed%20coffee%20from%20the%20plantations%20is%20among%20the%20main%20attractions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dso